#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:561
msgid ""
"OTRS has a large user community. Users and developers discuss OTRS and "
"exchange information on related issues through the <link linkend="
"\"additional-resources-mailinglists\">mailing-lists</link>.  You can use the "
"mailing lists to discuss installation, configuration, usage, localization "
"and development of OTRS. You can report software bugs in our <link linkend="
"\"additional-resources-bugtracking\">bug tracking system</link>."
msgstr ""
"OTRS ina jamii kubwa ya watumiaji. Watumiaji na watengenezaji wanajadili "
"OTRS na kubadilishana taarifa kuhusu maswaka husika kupitia <link linkend="
"\"additional-resources-mailinglists\">orodha ya watumiwa</link>. Unaweza "
"kutumia orodha ya watumiwa kujadili usakinishaji, usanidi, matumizi, undani "
"na uendelezaji wa OTRS. Unaweza kuripoti makosa ya programu katika <link "
"linkend=\"additional-resources-bugtracking\">mfumo wetu wa kufuatilia "
"makosa</link>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/introduction/otrs.xml:570
msgid ""
"The homepage of the OTRS community is: <ulink url=\"http://www.otrs.com/open-"
"source/\"><citetitle>http://www.otrs.com/open-source/</citetitle></ulink>."
