#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:517
msgid "\"Recoding the demand\" (AD1)"
msgstr "\"Kurekodi mahitaji\" (AD1)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:519
msgid ""
"An Activity Dialog that contains all the required fields for the data to be "
"collected for the order (Title, Author and ISBN), and a Status field with "
"the possibility to choose \"Approval\"."
msgstr ""
"Maongezi ya Shughuli yenye sehemu zote zinazoitajika ili data ikusanywe kwa "
"oda (Kichwa cha  habari, Mwandishi na ISBN), na sehemu ya Haliyenye "
"uwezekano wa kuchagua \"Kibali\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:525
msgid "\"Approval denied\" (AD2)"
msgstr "\"Kibali kimekataliwa\" (AD2)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:527
msgid ""
"An Activity Dialog with a comment field (Article) and a Status field with "
"the option \"Approval denied\"."
msgstr ""
"Maongezi ya Shughuli yenye sehemu ya kuweka maoni (Makala) na sehemu ya Hali "
"yenye chaguo \"Kibali kimekataliwa\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:532
msgid "\"Approved\" (AD3)"
msgstr "\"Kubaliwa\" (AD3)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:534
msgid "Here we just need the Status field with the option \"Approved\"."
msgstr "Hapa tunahitaji hali ya uga wenye chaguo \"Kubaliwa\""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:538
msgid "\"Order denied\" (AD4)"
msgstr "\"Oda imekataliwa\" (AD4)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:540
msgid ""
"An activity dialog which makes it possible for purchasing to reject an "
"impossible order (book out of stock). Here we also need a comment field and "
"the Status field with the option \"Order denied\"."
msgstr ""
"Maongezi ya shughuli yanayowezesha kununua ili kukataa oda isiyowezekana "
"(kulipia mzigo kabla ikiwa hisa zimeisha). Hapa pia tunahitaji sehemu ya "
"maoni na sehemu ya Hali yenye chaguo \"Oda imekataliwa\""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:546
msgid "\"Order placed\" (AD5)"
msgstr "\"Oda imewekwa\" (AD5)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:548
msgid ""
"An activity dialog with the fields Supplier, Price and Delivery date for "
"purchasing and the Status field with the option \"Order placed\"."
msgstr ""
"Maongezi ya Shughuli yenye sehemu Msambazaji, Bei na tarehe ya Uwasilishaji "
"kwa manunuzi na sehemu ya Hali yenye chaguo \"Oda imewekwa\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:553
msgid "\"Shipment received\" (AD6)"
msgstr "\"Vilivyosafirishwa vimepokelewa\" (AD6)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:555
msgid ""
"An activity for the mail room with a field for the Date of receipt and the "
"Status field with the option \"Shipment received\"."
msgstr ""
"Shughuli ya kwenye chumba cha barua yenye sehemu ya Tarehe ya upokeaji na "
"sehemu ya Hali yenye chaguo \"Vilivyosafirishwa vimepokelewa\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:562
msgid ""
"To restrict the Status field for each activity dialog we need to add some "
"ACLs in the Kernel/Config.pm or to a new perl file located in Kernel/Config/"
