#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1975
msgid "StartActivity"
msgstr "AnzaShughuli"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1977
msgid ""
"When creating a new process ticket, a StartActivity must be defined. As soon "
"as the ticket is created, this Activity will be set and used as the base for "
"the first transition checks."
msgstr ""
"Wakati wa kutengeneza mchakato mpya wa tiketi, lazima ufafanue ki "
"AnzaShughuli. Mara tu tiketi itakapotengenezwa, hiishughuli ita setiwa na "
"kutumika kama msingi wa kaguzi za kwanza za mpito."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1983
msgid "StartActivityDialog"
msgstr "AnzaShughuliMaongezi"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1985
msgid ""
"For new process tickets, a StartActivityDialog must be defined. This will be "
"shown when creating a new process ticket (after the process was selected). "
"At this point, the ticket does not exist yet, it will be created after "
"submitting the StartActivityDialog."
msgstr ""
"Kwa tiketi mpya, ki AnzaShughuliMaongezi lazima kifafanuliwe. Hii "
"itaonyeshwa wakati wa kutengeneza mchakato mpya wa tiketi (baada ya mchakato "
"kuchaguliwa). Hapa tiketi bado haipo, itatengenezwa baada ya kuwasilisha ki "
"AnzaShughuliMaongezi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1992
msgid "Path"
msgstr "Njia"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1994
msgid ""
"The Path contains the structure of the Activities, and the possible "
"Transitions between them, for the current process. And also the Transition "
"Actions that happens when transitioning . This controls the way that a "
"process ticket can take. Example:"
msgstr ""
"Njia ina muundo wa Shughuli, na Mapito yanayowezekana kati yao, kwa ajili ya "
"mchakato wa sasa.  Na pia Vitendo vya Mpito ambavyo vinatokea wakati wa "
"Mpito. Hii inadhibiti mwelekeo ambao tiketi ya mchakato itachukua. Mfano:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2001
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"'A1' => {\n"
"    'T1' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A2',\n"
"    },\n"
"    'T2' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A3',\n"
"    },\n"
"    'T3' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A4',\n"
"        TransitionAction => ['TA1', 'TA2'],\n"
"    },\n"
"},\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"'A1' => {\n"
"    'T1' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A2',\n"
"    },\n"
"    'T2' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A3',\n"
"    },\n"
"    'T3' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A4',\n"
"        TransitionAction => ['TA1', 'TA2'],\n"
"    },\n"
"},\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2016
msgid ""
"If a process ticket is in Activity 'A1', it has three possible ways to get "
"to another Activity. In the Transitions 'T1' to 'T3', conditions are "
"defined, that a process ticket must fulfill to move (transit) to another "
"Activity."
msgstr ""
"Kama tiketi ya mchakato iko kwenye shughuli 'A1', ina njia tatu "
"zinazowezekana kwenda kwenye Shughuli nyingine. Kwenye Mapito 'T1' kwenda "
"'T3', masharti yamefafanuliwa, ambayo tiketi ya mchakato inabidi iyatimize "
"ili ihamie kwenye Shughuli nyingine."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2021
msgid ""
"If in this case all the values of the process ticket and its dynamic fields "
"that are needed for the Transition 'T2' are correct, the ticket will be "
"moved from Activity 'A1' to 'A3'. After an ActivityDialog is submitted, or "
"any other change is made to a ticket, it will be checked for possible "
"Transitions from the current Activity. If multiple Transitions are possible, "
"the first one will be used (based on nummerical sorting of the "
"TransitionIDs)."
msgstr ""
"Kama katika kesi hii thamani zote za tiketi ya mchakato na sehemu zake "
"zinazobadilika ambazo zinahitajika kwa Mpito 'T2' ziko sawa, tiketi "
"itahamishwa kutoka Shughuli 'A1' kwenda 'A3'. Baada ya MaongeziYaShughuli "
"kuwasilishwa, au mabadiliko yoyote mengine yamefanywa kwenye tiketi, "
"itakaguliwa kwa Mapito yawezekanayo kutoka kwenye Shughuli ya sasa. Kama "
"Mapito zaidi ya moja yanawezekana, ya kwanza yatatumika (kutegemea na "
"upangaji wa nambari za Vitambulisho vya Mpito)."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2029
msgid ""
"Additionally, it is possible to assign Transition Actions to Transitions in "
"the Path configuration. These are modules which are executed after a "
"successful Transition. They have to be specified in array form as in the "
"example, we'll talk about the details later."
msgstr ""
"Kwa nyongeza, inawezekana kugawia Vitendo vya Mpito kwa Mapito katika "
"usanidi wa Njia. Hizi moduli ambazo zinatekelezwa baada ya mpito "
"uliofanikiwa. Inabidi zibainishwe katika fomu ya mkusanyiko kama kwenye "
"mfano, tutaongelea kwa undani baadaye."

