#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2583
msgid ""
"Example of a field name. The following ticket fields can be used: "
"<placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Mfina wa jina la sehemu. Sehemu zifwatazo za tiketi zinaweza kutumika: "
"<placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2612
msgid ""
"When testing a field with 'ID' (like SLAID), the database ID of the field "
"will be used for testing, for other fields (like SLA) the actual value is "
"used for testing."
msgstr ""
"Wakati wa kujaribisha sehemu kwa 'Kitambulisho' (kama Kitambulisho cha SLA), "
"Kitambulisho cha hifadhidata ya sehemu kitatumika kwa ajili ya majaribio, "
"kwa sehemu nyingine (kama SLA) thamani halisi inatumika kwa ajili ya "
"majaribio."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2620
msgid "Determines the kind of field testing. Possible values:"
msgstr "Inaamua aina ya kipimo cha eneo. Thamani ziwezekanazo:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2625
msgid ""
"'String': Compares the field value with the string specified in 'Match'. "
"Matches if they are exactly the same."
msgstr ""
"'Tungo': Inalinganisha thamani ya sehemu na tungo iliyobainishwa katika "
"'Lingana'. Zinalingana kama ziko sawa kabisa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2631
msgid ""
"'Hash': Compares the field value (hash) with the hash specified in 'Match'. "
"All hash values must be the same."
msgstr ""
"'Hash': Inafananisha thamani ya sehemu (hash) na hash iliyobainishwa kwenye "
"'Fananisha'. Thamani zote za hash lazima ziwe sawa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2637
msgid ""
"'Array': Compares the field value (array) with the array specified in "
"'Match'. Both lists must be the same."
msgstr ""
"'Mkusanyiko': Inalinganisha thamani ya sehemu (mkusanyiko) na mkusanyiko "
"uliobainishwa kwenye 'Lingana'. Orodha zote mbili lazima ziwe sawa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2643
msgid ""
"'Regex': The field value can be tested with a regular expression. It is "
"important that 'Match' contains <emphasis>qr{}xms</emphasis> as a base "
"condition. Between the braces the actual regular expression can be noted."
msgstr ""
"'Regex': Thamani ya sehemu inaweza kujaribiwa na usemi wa kawaida. Nimuhimu "
"kwamba 'Fanana' ina <emphasis>qr{}xms</emphasis> kama sharti la msingi. "
"Katikati ya mabano semi ya kawaida halisi inaweza kuandikwa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2651
msgid ""
"'Module': Allows you to use a perl module for condition checking. If it "
"returns 1, the check was positive. You can find an example module in "
"<filename>Kernel/System/ProcessManagement/TransitionValidation/ValidateDemo."
"pm</filename>."
msgstr ""
"'Moduli': Inakuruhusu kutumia moduli ya Perl kwa ajili ya kukagua masharti. "
"Kama ikirudisha 1, ukaguzi ulikua chanya. Unaweza kupata moduli ya mfano "
"kwenye <filename>Kernel/System/ProcessManagement/TransitionValidation/"
"ValidateDemo.pm</filename>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2666
msgid ""
"Transition Actions are actions which can be triggered after successfully "
"applied transitions (when a process ticket moves from one activity to "
"another). These Transition Actions can be used to perform different changes "
"on the ticket, e. g.  change the Queue or the Owner of the ticket, and you "
"can also create your own Transition Actions to perform other complex changes."
msgstr ""
"Vitendo vya Mpito ni vitendo ambavyo vinaweza kuchochewa baada ya mapito "
"yaliyofanyika kikamilifu (pale tiketi ya mchakato inapohama kutoka shughuli "
"moja hadi nyingine). Vitendo hivi vya Mpito vinaweza kutumika kufanya "
"mabadiliko mengi kwenye tiketi, mf. badilisha Foleni au Mmiliki wa tiketi, "
"na pia unaweza kutengeneza Vitendo vyako vya Mpito kufanya mabadiliko "
"mengine magumu."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2673
msgid "Transition Action configuration"
msgstr "Usanidi wa Vitendo vya Mpito"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2677
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Queue Move',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Queue  => 'Junk',\n"
"            UserID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Queue Move',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Queue  => 'Junk',\n"
"            UserID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

