"Kwa usaidizi kutoka ACLs, unaweza kuweka kikomo cha vitu vya kuchaguliwa "
"kwenye tiketi za mchakato. Tafadhali ona pia <link linkend=\"acl-reference"
"\">rejea ya ACL</link> kwa maelezo kamili ya sintaksi ya ACL."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3432
msgid "ACL configuration"
msgstr "Usanidi wa ACL"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3434
msgid ""
"ACLs can only be defined in <filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename>. Example:"
msgstr ""
"ACL zinaweza kufafanuliwa kwenye <filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename> tu. "
"Mfano:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3438
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-ProcessProperties'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Process => {\n"
"            ProcessEntityID        => ['P1'],\n"
"            ActivityEntityID       => ['A1'],\n"
"            ActivityDialogEntityID => ['AD1'],\n"
"        }\n"
