"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-ProcessProperties'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Process => {\n"
"            ProcessEntityID        => ['P1'],\n"
"            ActivityEntityID       => ['A1'],\n"
"            ActivityDialogEntityID => ['AD1'],\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3457
msgid "001-ACL-ProcessProperties"
msgstr "001-ACL-SifaMchakato"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3459
msgid ""
"Name of the ACL rule. For further information on ACL rules in general, "
"please consult <link linkend=\"acl\">the ACL manual</link>."
msgstr ""
"Jina la sheria ya ACL. Kwa maelezo zaidi kuhusu sheria za ACL kwa ujumla, "
"tafadhali nenda <link linkend=\"acl\">mwongozo wa ACL</link>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3466
msgid ""
"This is the section that is used to check if an ACL must be applied. If it "
"has the specified values, the rule is applied. The following values can be "
"used:"
msgstr ""
"Hii sehemu inatumika lulagua kama ACL laizma itumike. Kama ina thamani "
"zilizowekwa bayana, sheria itatumika. Thamani zifuatazo zinaweza kutumika:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3470
msgid "ProcessEntityID"
msgstr "KitambulishoChaChomboChaMchakato"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3472
msgid ""
"The ID of a process that the process. Matches if the ticket is assigned to "
"this process."
msgstr ""
"Kitambulisho cha mchakato ambacho mchakato. Unafanania kama tiketi ikigawiwa "
"kwa huu mchakato. "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3477
msgid "ActivityEntityID"
msgstr "KitambulishoChaChomboChaShughuli"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3479
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity that the process ticket currently is assigned to."
msgstr ""
"Kitambulisho cha Shughuli ambayo tiketi ya mchakato imegawiwa kwa sasa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3483
msgid "ActivityDialogEntityID"
msgstr "KitambulishoChaChomboChaMaongeziYaShughuli"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3485
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity Dialog that is currently open for a process ticket."
msgstr ""
"Kitambulisho cha Maongezi ya Shughuli ambayo yako wazi kwa tiketi ya "
"mchakato kwa sasa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3490
msgid "Possible/PossibleNot Activity Dialog"
msgstr "Ynayowezekana/Yasiyowezekana Maongezi ya Shughuli"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3492
msgid ""
"Here you can specify a list of Activity Dialog IDs. This list will limit the "
"possible Activity Dialogs that are offered to the user in the ticket zoom "
"mask."
msgstr ""
"Hapa unaweza kuweka bayana orodha ya Vitambulisho vya Maongezi ya Shughuli. "
"Hii orodha itaweka ukomo wa Maongezi ya Shughuli ambayo yanaweza kugawiwa "
"kwa mtumijai katika barakoa ya kuza tiketi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3496
msgid ""
"'Possible' lists the Activity Dialogs that are allowed. The setting above "
"will only allow 'AD1' and 'AD3' of the list of configured Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"'Inawezekana' inaorodhesha Maongezi ya Shughuli ambayo yanaruhusiwa. "
"Mpangilio hapo juu utaruhusu 'AD1' na 'AD3' tu kati ya orodha ya Maongezi ya "
"Shughuli yaliyosanidiwa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3500
msgid ""
"'PossibleNot' lists the Activity Dialogs that are not allowed. In the "
"example above, the setting will remove 'AD3' from the list of configured "
"Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"'InawezekanaHapana' inaorodhesha Maongezi ya Shughuli ambayo hayaruhusiwi. "
"Katika mfano hapo juu, mpangilio utaondoa 'AD3' kutoka kwenye orodha ya "
"Maongezi ya Shughuli yaliyosanidiwa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3505
msgid ""
"If both 'Possible' and 'PossibleNot' are specified, the list of configured "
"Activity Dialogs will first be filtered by 'Possible', leaving only 'AD1' "
"and 'AD3' in our example. Then 'PossibleNot' will be applied and filter out "
"'AD3', so that only 'AD1' remains and is shown as a possible Activity Dialog "
"that the user can use."
msgstr ""
"Kama zote 'Inawezekana' na 'InawezekanaHapana' zimewekwa bayana, orodha ya "
"Maongezi ya Shughuli yatachujwa kwanza na 'Inawezekana', na kuacha 'AD1' na "
"'AD3' tu katika mfano wetu. Kisha 'InawezekanaHapana' itafanyika na kuchuja "
"'AD3', ili 'AD1' pekee ibaki na inaonyeshwa kama Maongezi ya Shughuli "
"yanayowezekana ambayo mtumiaji anaweza kutumia."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3512
msgid ""
"If multiple ACL rules match, the intersection of all matching rules will be "
"calculated to determine the possible Activity Dialogs. Example:"
msgstr ""
"Kama sheria zaidi ya moja za ACL zimefanana, muunganiko wa sheria zote "
"zinazofanana utatafutwa kutengeneza Maongezi ya Shughuli yanayowezekana. "
"Mfano:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3518
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'003-ACL-Priority'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Priority => ['3 normal']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3', 'AD4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'003-ACL-Priority'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Priority => ['3 normal']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3', 'AD4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3516
msgid ""
"Configured Activity Dialogs: 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD5', 'AD6', "
"'AD7'.  <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Maongezi ya Shughuli Yaliyosanidiwa: 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD5', "
"'AD6', 'AD7'.  <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3551
msgid ""
"If a process ticket has the state 'new', is in the 'Raw' queue and has a "
"priority '3 normal', then all three ACL rules will match."
msgstr ""
"Kama tiketi ya mchakato ina hali 'mpya', iko kwenye foleni 'Mbichi' na ina "
"kipaumbele '3 kawaida', basi sheria zote tatu za ACL zitafanana nayo."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3555
msgid ""
"The first rule reduces the Activity Dialogs from 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', "
"'AD5', 'AD6', 'AD7' to 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7' and forbids 'AD4' "
"and 'AD5'."
msgstr ""
"Sheria ya kwanza inapunguza Maongezi ya Shughuli kutoka 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', "
"'AD4', 'AD5', 'AD6', 'AD7' to 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7' na inakataza "
"'AD4' na 'AD5'."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3560
msgid ""
"The second rule will now further reduce the remaining Activity Dialogs.  In "
"our example, 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD7' will remain."
msgstr ""
"Sheria ya pili itapunguza zaidi Maongezi ya Shughuli yaliyobaki. Katika "
"mfano wetu, 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD7' zitabaki."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3564
msgid ""
"Now the third rule will further reduce the list by 'PossibleNot'.  'AD3' is "
"removed from the list. 'AD4' is not removed, since it was not on the list in "
"the first place. At the end, 'AD2' and 'AD7' remain as possible Activity "
"Dialogs that the user can utilize."
msgstr ""
"Sasa sheria ya tatu itapunguza zaidi orodha kwa 'InawezekanaHapana'. 'AD3' "
"inaondolewa kutoka kwenye orodha. 'AD4' haiondolewi, kwa kuwa haikuwa kwenye "
"orodha tangu mwanzo. Mwishoni, 'AD2' na 'AD7' zitabaki kama Maongezi ya "
"Shughuli yanayowezekana ambayo mtumiaji anaweza kutumia."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3570
msgid ""
"It is also possible to limit the processes that can be displayed in the "
"\"New process ticket\" screen, the functionality is similar to limiting the "
"ActivityDialogs with one exception: The ACLs could only be based on Users."
msgstr ""
"Pia inawezekana kuweka ukomo wa michakato ambayo inaweza kuonyeshwa katika "
"skrini ya \"Tiketi mpya ya mchakato\", hii sifa ni sawa na kuweka ukomo wa "
"MaongeziYaShughuli kwa ubaguzi mmoja: ACL zinaweza kujikita kwa watumiaji tu."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3574
msgid "See examples below:"
msgstr "Ona mifano chini:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3577
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'200-ACL-Process'} = {\n"
"    # match properties\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        User => {\n"
"            UserID => [2, 3],\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"       Process => ['P1', 'P2', 'P3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        Process => ['P4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'200-ACL-Process'} = {\n"
"    # match properties\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        User => {\n"
"            UserID => [2, 3],\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"       Process => ['P1', 'P2', 'P3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        Process => ['P4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3595
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'201-ACL-Process'} = {\n"
"    # match properties\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        User => {\n"
"            Group_rw => [ 'MyGroup' ],\n"
"        },\n"
