#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:21
msgid "TicketIndexModule"
msgstr "ModuliKielelezoTiketi"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:23
msgid "There are two backend modules for the ticket index:"
msgstr "Kuna moduli mbili za mazingira ya nyuma ya kielelezo cha tiketi:"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:31
msgid ""
"Using Kernel::System::Ticket::IndexAccelerator::RuntimeDB (default), "
"generate each queue view on the fly from the ticket table. You will not have "
"performance trouble until you have about 60,000 open tickets in your system."
msgstr ""
"Kwa kutumia Kernel::System::Ticket::IndexAccelerator::RuntimeDB (chaguo-"
"msingi), zalisha kila muonekano moja kwa moja kutoka kwenye jedwali la "
"tiketi. Hautakuwa na matatizo ya kiutendaji mpaka labda ukiwa na tiketi "
"60,000 zilizofunguliwa kwenye mfumo wako."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:37
msgid ""
"Kernel::System::Ticket::IndexAccelerator::StaticDB, the most powerful "
"module, should be used when you have above 80,000 open tickets. It uses an "
"extra ticket_index table, which works like a view. Use <filename>bin/otrs."
"RebuildTicketIndex.pl</filename> for generating an initial index build after "
"switching backends."
msgstr ""
"Kiini::Mfumo::Tiketi::KielezoKiharakishi::DBTuli, moduli yenye nguvu "
"kushinda zote, inatakiwa kutumika wakati una tiketi zilizo wazi zaidi ya "
"80,000. Inatumia jedwali la ziada la tiketi_kielezo., ambayo inafanyakazi "
"kama muonekano. Tumia <filename>bin/otrs.RebuildTicketIndex.pl</filename> "
"kuzalisha kielezo kijenzi cha mwanzo baada ya kubadilisha mazingira ya nyuma."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:45
msgid "You can change the IndexAccelerator via SysConfig."
msgstr "Unaweza kubadilisha IndexAccelerator kupitia SysConfig."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:51
msgid "TicketStorageModule"
msgstr "ModuliHifadhiTiketi"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:53
msgid "There are two different backend modules for the ticket/article storage:"
msgstr ""
"Kuna moduli mbili tofauti za mazingira ya nyuma ya uhifadhi wa tiketi/makala:"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:61
msgid ""
"Configure Kernel::System::Ticket::ArticleStorageDB (default) to store "
"attachments, etc., in the database. Note: Don't use it with large set ups."
msgstr ""
"Sanidi Kernel::System::Ticket::ArticleStorageDB (chaguo-msingi) kuhifadhi "
"viambatanishi, na kadh., katika hifadhidata. Tambua: Usitumie na mipangilio "
"mkubwa."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:64
msgid ""
"Pro: If your webserver user isn't the 'otrs' user, use this module to avoid "
"file permission problems."
msgstr ""
"Faida: Kama mtumiaji wako wa seva ya tovuti siyo mtumiaji wa 'otrs', tumia "
"hii moduli kuzuia matatizo ya ruhusa za faili."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:67
msgid ""
"Con: It is not advisable to store attachments in your database. Take care "
"that your database is able to store large objects. E.g. Configure MySQL with "
"\"set-variable = max_allowed_packet=8M\" to store 8 MB objects (the default "
"is 2M)."
msgstr ""
"Hasara: Haishauriwi kuhifadhi viambatanisho kwenye hifadhidata yako. Chukua "
"tahadhari kwamba hifadhidata yako inaweza kuhifadhi vitu vikubwa. Mf. Sanidi "
"MySQL na \"set-variable = max_allowed_packet=8M\" kuhifadhi vitu vyenye 8 MB "
"(chaguo msingi ni 2M)."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:73
msgid ""
"Configure Kernel::System::Ticket::ArticleStorageFS to store attachments etc. "
"on the local file system. Note: Recommended for large setups."
msgstr ""
"Sanidi Kernel::System::Ticket::ArticleStorageFS kuhifadhi viambatanishi na "
"kadh. katika mfumo wa faili wa ndani. Tambua: Inashauriwa kwa mipangilio "
"mikubwa"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:76
msgid "Pro: It is fast!"
msgstr "Faida: Ni ya kasi!"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:79
msgid ""
"Con: Your web server user should be the 'otrs' user. Also, if you have "
"multiple front-end servers, you should make sure the filesystem is shared "
"between the servers. Place it on an NFS share or preferably a SAN or similar "
"solution."
msgstr ""
"Hasara: Mtumiaji wako wa seva ya tovuti anatakiwa kuwa mtumiaji wa 'otrs'. "
"Pia, kama una seva za mazingira ya mbele zaidi ya moja, unatakiwa "
"kuhakikisha mfumo wa faili unatumiwa kwa pamoja kati ya seva. Iweke kwenye "
"ushirika wa NFS au kwa mapendeleo zaidi SAN au inayofanania."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:88
msgid ""
"Note: you can switch from one back-end to the other on the fly. You can "
"switch the backend in the SysConfig, and then run the command line utility "
"<filename>otrs.ArticleStorageSwitch.pl</filename> to put the articles from "
"the database onto the filesystem or the other way around. You can use the "
"<emphasis>-s</emphasis> and <emphasis>-d</emphasis> options to specify the "
"source and destination back-ends. Please note that the entire process can "
"take considerable time to run, depending on the number of articles you have "
"and the available CPU power and/or network capacity."
msgstr ""
"Kumbuka: unaweza kubadilisha kutoka aina moja ya mazingira ya nyuma kwenda "
"mengine kwa haraka, Unaweza kubadilisha mazingira ya nyuma katika SysConfig, "
"baada ya hapo anzisha zana ya tungo amri <filename>otrs.ArticleStorageSwitch."
"pl</filename> ili kuweka makala kutoka kwenye hifadhidata kwenda kwenye "
"mfumo wa mafaili na kinyume chake. Unaweza kutumia machaguo <emphasis>-s</"
"emphasis> na <emphasis>-d</emphasis> kuweka bayana chanzo na kifikio cha "
"mazingira ya nyuma. Tafadhali tambua mchakato mzima unaweza kutumia muda "
"mwingi kufanyika, kutegemeana na idadi ya makala ulizonazo na uwezo wa "
"kitengo kikuu cha uchakataji na/au uwezo wa mtandao."

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "shell> bin/otrs.ArticleStorageSwitch.pl -s ArticleStorageDB -d ArticleStorageFS\n"
msgstr "shell> bin/otrs.ArticleStorageSwitch.pl -s ArticleStorageDB -d ArticleStorageFS\n"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:97
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Script: Switching storage back-ends from database to filesystem.</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Hati: Kubadilisha mazingira ya nyuma ya hifadhi kutoka hifadhidata "
"kuwa mfumo wa mafaili</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:102
msgid "Archiving Tickets"
msgstr "Kuhifadhi Tiketi"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:105
msgid ""
"As OTRS can be used as an audit-proof system, deleting closed tickets may "
"not be a good idea. Therefore we implemented a feature that allows you to "
"archive tickets."
msgstr ""
"Kwa kuwa OTRS inaweza kutumika kama mfumo wa kuzuia ukaguzi, kufuta tiketi "
"zilizofungwa inaweza kuwa sio wazo zuri. Kwa hiyo tumetengeneza kipengele "
"kinachokuruhusu kuhifadhi tiketi kwenye nyaraka."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:108
msgid ""
"Tickets that match certain criteria can be marked as \"archived\" These "
"tickets are not accessed if you do a regular ticket search or run a Generic "
"Agent job. The system itself does not have to deal with a huge amount of "
"tickets any longer as only the \"latest\" tickets are taken into "
"consideration when using OTRS. This can result in a huge performance gain on "
"large systems."
msgstr ""
"Tiketi zinazofanana na vigezo fulani zinaweza kuwekewa alama kama \"zilizo "
"kwenye nyaraka\". Hizi tiketi haziwezi kupatikana kama ukifanya utafutaji "
"tiketi wa kawaida au kuanzisha kazi ya Wakala wa Ujumla. Mfumo wenyewe "
"hautahangaika na idadi kubwa yatiketi tena kwa sababu tiketi za hivi "
"karibuni tu ndio zinatiliwa maanani na OTRS. Hii inaweza kuleta ufanisi "
"mkubwa katika mifumo mikubwa. "

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:111
