"literal>. In <literal>Core::Ticket</literal> you find the option "
"<literal>Ticket::ArchiveSystem</literal> which is set to \"no\" by default. "
"Change this setting to \"yes\" and save this change."
msgstr ""
"Katika kurasa ya msimamizi, nenda kwenye AysConfig na chagua "
"<literal>Tiketi</literal> ya kundi hilo. Katika <literal>Kiini::Tiketi</"
"literal> unakuta chaguo <literal>Tiketi::MfumoNyaraka</literal> ambao "
"umesetiwa kuwa \"hapana\" kwa chaguo-msingi. Badilisha mpangilio huu kuwa "
"\"ndiyo\" na hifadhi mabadiliko."

