#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:282
msgid "Pre-established database connections"
msgstr "Miunganiko ya hifadhidata iliyotengenezwa."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:284
msgid ""
"You can have the database connections pre-established on startup of the web "
"server. This saves time (see README.webserver)."
msgstr ""
"Una miunganiko ya hifadhidata imewekwa tayari wakati wauanzishwaji wa seva "
"ya tovuti. Hii inaokoa muda (pitia README.webserver)."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:289
msgid "Preloaded modules - startup.pl"
msgstr "Moduli zilizopakiwa tayari -startup.pl"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:291
msgid ""
"Use the startup script <filename>scripts/apache2-perl-startup.pl</filename> "
"for preloaded/precompiled Perl modules on your mod_perl webserver to be "
"faster, with a smaller memory footprint (see README.webserver)."
msgstr ""
"Tumia hati ya uwashaji <filename>scripts/apache2-perl-startup.pl</filename> "
"kwa ajili ya moduli za Perl ambazo tayari zimepakiwa/zimekusanywa-zalishwa "
"katika seva yajo ya tovuti ya mod_perl kuwa ya kasi zaidi, kwa utumiaji "
"mdogo wa kumbukumbu (ona README.webserver)."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:295
msgid "Reload Perl modules when updated on disk"
msgstr "Pakia tena moduli za perl zinapo sasishwa kwnye diski"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:297
msgid ""
"By default Apache::Reload is used in scripts/apache2-httpd.include.conf. "
"Disable it and you will get 8% more speed. But remember to restart the web "
"server if you install any modules via the OTRS Package Manager, or any "
"values in your SysConfig or in Kernel/Config.pm. Important: this would also "
"mean you can't use the OTRS Package Manager via the web interface, you need "
"to use the command line variant - <filename>bin/otrs.PackageManager.pl</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"Kwa kawaida Apache::Reload inatumika katika scripts/apache2-httpd.include."
"conf. Ilemaze na utapata ongezeko la kasi kwa 8% zaidi. Lakini kumbuka "
"kuanzisha upya seva ya tovuti kama ukisakinisha moduli zozote kupitia Meneja "
"Kifurushi wa OTRS, au thamani zozote katika SysConfig yako  au katika Kernel/"
"Config.pm. Muhimu: hii inamaanisha pia huwezi kutumia Meneja Kifurushi wa "
"OTRS kupitia kiolesura cha tovuti, unahitaji kutumia lahaja ya tungo amri - "
"<filename>bin/otrs.PackageManager.pl</filename>."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:302
msgid "Choosing the Right Strategy"
msgstr "Kuchagua mkakati sahihi"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:304
msgid ""
"If you have a larger installation, e.g. over 1,000 new tickets per day and "
"over 40 agents, it is a good idea to read the chapters on Performance of the "
"mod_perl User's Guide ( <ulink url=\"http://perl.apache.org/docs/2.0/user/"
"index.html\"><citetitle>http://perl.apache.org/docs/2.0/user/index.html</"
"citetitle></ulink> )."
msgstr ""
"Kama una usakinishaji mkubwa, mf. zaidi ya tiketi mpya 1,000 kwa siku na "
"zaidi ya mawakala 40, ni wazo zuri kusoma sura kuhusu Utendaji katika "
"Mwongozo wa Mtumiaji wa mod_perl  ( <ulink url=\"http://perl.apache.org/"
"docs/2.0/user/index.html\"><citetitle>http://perl.apache.org/docs/2.0/user/"
"index.html</citetitle></ulink> )."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:309
msgid "mod_gzip/mod_deflate"
msgstr "mod_gzip/mod_deflate"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/content/performance-tuning.xml:311
msgid ""
"If your bandwidth is small, use mod_deflate for Apache2. If you have an html "
"page with 45k, mod_gzip/mod_deflate compresses it to about 7k. The drawback "
"is that this increases the load on the server side."
msgstr ""
"Kama kipimo data chako ni kidogo, tumia mod_deflate kwa ajili ya Apache2. "
"Kama una ukurasa wa html wenye 45k, mod_gzip/mod_deflate itaufinyaza kuwa "
"takribani 7k. Hasara ni kwamba hii inaongeza mzigo kwenye upande wa seva."

#. type: Content of: <preface><title>
