"na OTRS (mf. mazingira ya nyuma ya LDAP na hifadhidata), parameta ya usanidi "
"ya MtejaMtumiaji lazima ipanuliwe na nambari, mf. \"MtejaMtumiaji 1\", "
"\"MtejaMtumiaji2\" (ona Mfano 11-5 chini)."

