"kiotomatiki kwa kutumia mfumo wa uendeshaji. Hati hizo zinapatikana chini ya "
"OTRS_NYUMBANI/hati."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:129
