#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:316
msgid "Scheduler Service Installer"
msgstr "Kisanikishi cha Huduma za Mratibu"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:318
msgid ""
"On Windows, the OTRS Scheduler is registered as a Service via the Windows "
"Service Control Manager (SCM). In order to have the OTRS Scheduler process "
"to be controlled by the SCM is necessary to register this service.  If you "
"used the Windows Installer this is taken care of by the installer, and there "
"are no manual actions required."
msgstr ""
"Katika Windows, Mratibu wa OTRS amesajiliwa kama mchakato kupitia Meneja "
"Udhibiti wa Huduma wa Windows (SCM). Ili kuufanya mchakato wa Mratibu wa "
"OTRS kudhibitiwa na SCM ni muhimu kuanzisha huduma hii. Kama ulitumia "
"kisakinishi cha Windows hii itashughulikiwa na kisakinishi, na hakuna "
"vitendo vinavyohitajika visivyokuwa vya otomatiki. "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:325
msgid ""
"OTRS provides the script <command>OTRS_HOME/bin/otrs.Scheduler4WinInstaller."
"pl</command> to register or unregister the OTRS Scheduler into the SCM."
msgstr ""
"OTRS inatoa hati <command>OTRS_HOME/bin/otrs.Scheduler4WinInstaller.pl</"
"command> kusajili au kutosajili Mratibu wa OTRS kwenye SCM."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:331
msgid ""
"Registering and de-registering can only be performed by members of the "
"Administrator group on Windows. You might need to right-click on cmd.exe and "
"select 'Run as Administrator' before you can register the service correctly."
msgstr ""
"Kujisajili na kujiondoa vinaweza kufanywa na wanachama wa kundi la msimamizi "
"katika Windows. Unaweza kuhitaji kubofya kulia katika cmd.exe na kuchagua "
"'Anzisha kama Msimamizi' kabla ya kusajili huduma kwa usahihi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><example><title>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:337
msgid "Example to register the OTRS Scheduler as a Windows Service"
msgstr "Mfano kusajili Mratibu wa OTRS kama Huduma ya Windows"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><example><para><screen>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:340
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"                            shell> perl OTRS_HOME/bin/otrs.Scheduler4WinInstaller.pl -a install\n"
"                        "
msgstr ""
"                            shell> perl OTRS_HOME/bin/otrs.Scheduler4WinInstaller.pl -a install\n"
"                        "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:354
msgid ""
"<command>install</command>- to install the Scheduler process into the "
"Windows SCM."
msgstr ""
"<command>sakinisha</command>- kusakinisha mchakato wa Mratibu kweye Windows."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:360
msgid ""
"<command>remove</command>- to remove the Scheduler process from the Windows "
"SCM."
msgstr ""
"<command>ondoa</command>- kuondoa mchakato wa Mratibu kutoka kwenye Windows."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:368
msgid ""
"After installing into the Windows SCM the OTRS Scheduler process can be used "
"like any other service on Windows. It can be started, stopped and restarted "
"and can be configured to be started manually or automatic."
msgstr ""
"Baada ya usakinishaji kwenye Windows SCM mchakato wa Mratibu wa OTRS unaweza "
"kutumika kama mchakato mwingine wowote katika Windows. Unaweza kuanzishwa, "
"kusitishwa na kuanzishwa upya na inaweza kusanidiwa kuanzishwa kiotomatiki "
"au kwa mikono."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/scheduler.xml:374
msgid ""
"To learn more about Windows Services and the Windows SCM please read the "
"Windows documentation, and Microsoft online help."
msgstr ""
"Kujifunza zaidi kuhusu Huduma za Windows na Windows SCM tafadhali soma "
"nyaraka ya Windows, na usaidizi wa kwenye mtandao wa Microsoft."

