#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:12
msgid "Via Sendmail (default)"
msgstr "Kupitia TumaBaruapepe (chaguo-msingi)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:15
msgid ""
"OTRS can send out emails via <ulink url=\"http://www.sendmail.org/"
"\">Sendmail</ulink>, <ulink url=\"http://www.postfix.org/\">Postfix</ulink>, "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.qmail.org\">Qmail</ulink> or <ulink url=\"http://www."
"exim.org\">Exim</ulink>). The default configuration is to use Sendmail and "
"should work out-of-the-box."
msgstr ""
"OTRS inaweza kutuma nje barua pepe kupitia <ulink url=\"http://www.sendmail."
"org/\">Tumabarua</ulink>, <ulink url=\"http://www.postfix.org/\">Postfix</"
"ulink>, <ulink url=\"http://www.qmail.org\">Qmail</ulink> or <ulink url="
"\"http://www.exim.org\">Exim</ulink>). Usanidi chaguo-msingi ni kutumia "
"Tumabarua na inatakiwa kufanya kazi nje-ya-boksi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:19
msgid ""
"You can configure the sendmail settings via the graphical configuration "
"frontend (Framework::Core::Sendmail)"
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kusanidi mipangilio ya tumabarua kupitia mazingira ya mbele ya "
"usanidi michoro (Kiunzi::Kiini::Tumabarua)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:25
msgid "Via SMTP server or smarthost"
msgstr "Kupitia SMTP au smarthost"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:28
msgid ""
"OTRS can send emails via SMTP (<ulink url=\"http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc821."
"txt\">Simple Mail Transfer Protocol / RFC 821</ulink>) or Secure SMTP. You "
"will want to use this on non-UNIX platforms (e.g. Windows)."
msgstr ""
"OTRS inaweza kutuma barua pepe kupitia SMTP  (<ulink url=\"http://www.ietf."
"org/rfc/rfc821.txt\">Simple Mail Transfer Protocol / RFC 821</ulink>) au "
"SMTP iliyo salama. Utataka kutumia hii kwenye majukwaa yasiyo ya UNIX (mf. "
"Windows)."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:32
msgid ""
"The SMTP server settings can be configured via the SysConfig (Framework::"
"Core::Sendmail). If you don't see SMTPS available as an option, the required "
"Perl modules are missing. In that case, please refer to <link linkend="
"\"installation-of-perl-modules\">\"Installation of Perl modules required for "
"OTRS\"</link> for instructions."
msgstr ""
"Mipangilio ya SMTP seva inaweza kusanidiwa kupitia SysConfig (Kiunzi::Kiini::"
"Tumabarua). Kama huoni SMTP inayopatikana kama chaguo, moduli za perl "
"zinazotakiwa hazipo. Katika kesi hiyo tafadhali tembelea <link linkend="
"\"installation-of-perl-modules\">\"Usakinishaji wa moduli za Perl "
"zinazohitajika kwa aili ya OTRS\"</link> kwa maelekezo."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:40
msgid "Receiving emails"
msgstr "Kupokea barua pepe"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:43
msgid "Mail accounts configured via the OTRS GUI"
msgstr ""
"Akaunti za barua pepe zilizo sanidiwa kupitia kiolesura michoro cha mtumiaji "
"cha OTRS."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:46
msgid ""
"OTRS is able to receive emails from POP3, POP3S, IMAP, and IMAPS mail "
"accounts."
msgstr ""
"OTRS inaweza kupokea barua pepe kutoka akaunti za POP3, POP3S, IMAP, na "
"IMAPS."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:50
msgid ""
"Configure your mail accounts via the PostMaster Mail Accounts link on the "
"Admin page."
msgstr ""
"Sanidi akaunti zako za posta kupitia kiungo cha Akaunti za Posta za "
"MkuuWaPosta  kwenye ukurasa wa Msimamizi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:54
msgid ""
"If a new mail account is to be created (see Figure below), then its mail "
"server name, login name and password must be specified. Also, you need to "
"select the mail server type, which can be POP3, POP3S, IMAP or IMAPS. If you "
"don't see your server type available as an option, the required Perl modules "
"are missing on your system. In that case, please refer to <link linkend="
"\"installation-of-perl-modules\"> \"Installation of Perl modules required "
"for OTRS\"</link> for instructions."
msgstr ""
"Kama akaunti mpya ya barua inatakiwa kutengenezwa (ona Kielelezo chini), "
"basi jina lake la seva ya barua, jina la kuingilia na nywila lazima ziwekwe "
"bayana. Pia, unahitaji kuchagua aina ya seva ya barua, ambayo inaweza kuwa "
"POP3, POP3S, IMAP au IMAPS. Kama huoni aina yako ya seva kuwepo kama chaguo, "
"moduli za Perl zinazotakiwa hazipo katika mfumo wako. Katika kesi hiyo, "
"tafadhali nenda kwenye <link linkend=\"installation-of-perl-modules\"> "
"\"Usakinishaji wa moduli za Perl zinazohitajika na OTRS\"</link> kwa "
"maelekezo. "

