#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:114
msgid "If the email is shown in the QueueView, then your setup is working."
msgstr ""
"Kama barua pepe imeonyeshwa kwenye MuonekanoFoleni, basi mpangilio wako "
"unafanya kazi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:118
msgid ""
"Procmail is a very common e-mail filter in Linux environments. It is "
"installed on most systems. If not, have a look at the <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.procmail.org/\"><citetitle>procmail homepage</citetitle></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Procmail ni kichujio cha barua pepe kinachojulikana sana katika mazingira ya "
"Linux. Inasakinishwa katika mifumo mingi. Kama siyo, angalia katika <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.procmail.org/\"><citetitle>ukurasa wa nyumbani wa procmail</"
"citetitle></ulink>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:122
msgid ""
"To configure procmail for OTRS (based upon a procmail configured MTA such as "
"sendmail, postfix, exim or qmail), use the <filename>~otrs/.procmailrc.dist</"
"filename> file and copy it to <filename>.procmailrc</filename> and add the "
"lines of the script below."
msgstr ""
"Kusanidi procmail kwa ajili ya OTRS (kutegemeana na MTA iliyosanidiwa na "
"procmail kama sendmail, postfix, exim au qmail), tumia faili "
"<filename>~otrs/.procmailrc.dist</filename> na nakili kwenda kwenye "
"<filename>.procmailrc</filename> na ongeza mistari ya hati chini."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><programlisting>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:128
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"SYS_HOME=$HOME\n"
"PATH=/bin:/usr/bin:/usr/local/bin\n"
"# --\n"
"# Pipe all email into the PostMaster process.\n"
"# --\n"
":0 :\n"
"| $SYS_HOME/bin/otrs.PostMaster.pl\n"
msgstr ""
"SYS_HOME=$HOME\n"
"PATH=/bin:/usr/bin:/usr/local/bin\n"
"# --\n"
