"MuonekanoFoleni wako."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:149
msgid "Fetching emails via POP3 or IMAP and fetchmail for otrs.PostMaster.pl"
msgstr ""
"Kutafuta barua pepe kupitia POP3 au IMAP na kutafuta otrs.PostMaster.pl"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:152
msgid ""
"In order to get email from your mail server, via a POP3 or IMAP mailbox, to "
"the OTRS machine/local OTRS account and to procmail, use <ulink url=\"http://"
"fetchmail.berlios.de/\">fetchmail</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ili kupata barua pepe kutoka kwenye seva yako ya barua, kupitia kikasha "
"barua cha POP3 au IMAP, kwenda kwenye OTRS akaunti ya OTRS ya machine/local "
"na kwenye procmail, tumia <ulink url=\"http://fetchmail.berlios.de/"
"\">tafutabarua</ulink>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:157
msgid "A working SMTP configuration on the OTRS machine is required."
msgstr "Usanidi wa SMTP unaofanya kazi unahitajika kwenye mashine ya OTRS."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:162
msgid ""
"You can use the <filename>.fetchmailrc.dist</filename> in the home directory "
"of OTRS and copy it to <filename>.fetchmailrc</filename>. Modfiy/change it "
"for your needs (see the Example 7-1 below)."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kutumia <filename>.fetchmailrc.dist</filename> katika mpangilio "
"orodha wa nyumbani wa OTRS na kuunakili kwenda <filename>.fetchmailrc</"
"filename>. Iboreshe/Ibadilishe kwa mahitaji yako (ona Mfano 7-1 chini)."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><example><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:166
msgid ".fetchmailrc"
msgstr ".fetchmailrc"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><example><para><programlisting>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:170
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"#poll (mailserver) protocol POP3 user (user) password (password) is (localuser)\n"
"poll mail.example.com protocol POP3 user joe password mama is otrs\n"
msgstr ""
"#poll (mailserver) protocol POP3 user (user) password (password) is (localuser)\n"
"poll mail.example.com protocol POP3 user joe password mama is otrs\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:178
msgid ""
"Don't forget to set the .fetchmailrc to 710 (\"chmod 710 .fetchmailrc\")!"
msgstr "Usisahau kuseti .fetchmailrc kuwa 710 (\"chmod 710 .fetchmailrc\")!"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:182
msgid ""
"With the <filename>.fetchmailrc</filename> from the Example 7-1 above, all "
"email will be forwarded to the local OTRS account, if the command "
"<command>fetchmail -a</command> is executed. Set up a cronjob with this "
"command if you want to fetch the mails regularly."
msgstr ""
"Na <filename>.fetchmailrc</filename> kutoka kwenye Mfano 7-1 hapo juu, barua "
"pepe zote zitapelekwa mbele kwenye akaunti ya ndani ya OTRS, kama agizo "
"<command>fetchmail -a</command> limetekelezwa. Seti kazi ya mfumo "
"iliyopangwa na agizo hili kama ukitaka kutafuta barua mara kwa mara."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:188
msgid ""
"Filtering/dispatching by OTRS/PostMaster modules (for more complex "
"dispatching)"
msgstr ""
"Kuchuja/kutuma kwa moduli za OTRS/MkuuWaPosta (kwa ajili ya utumaji "
"changamano)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:191
msgid ""
"If you use the bin/otrs.PostMaster.pl or bin/otrs.PostMasterMailbox.pl "
"method, you can insert or modify X-OTRS header entries with the PostMaster "
"filter modules. With the X-OTRS headers, the ticket system can execute some "
"actions on incoming mails, sort them into a specific queue, change the "
"priority or change the customer ID, for example. More information about the "
"X-OTRS headers are available in the section about <link linkend=\"adminarea-"
"postmasterpop3-account\">adding mail accounts</link> from the OTRS Admin "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Kama ukitumia njia ya bin/otrs.PostMaster.pl au bin/otrs.PostMasterMailbox."
"pl, unaweza kuingiza au kubadilisha maingizo ya vichwa vya X-OTRS kwa "
"kutumia moduli za kuchuja za MkuuWaPosta. Na vichwa vya X-OTRS mfumo wa "
"tiketi unaweza kutekeleza baadhi ya  vitendo kwa barua zinazoingia, "
"kuzipanga kwenye foleni maalumu, kubadili kipaumbele au kubadili "
"kitambulisho cha mteja, kwa mfano. Taarifa zaidi kuhusu vichwa vya X-OTRS "
"zinapatikana katika kifungu kuhusu <link linkend=\"adminarea-postmasterpop3-"
"account\">kuongeza akaunti za barua</link>kutoka kwenye kurasa ya Msimamizi "
"wa OTRS."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:196
msgid "There are some default filter modules:"
msgstr "Kuna baadhi ya moduli chaguo-msingi za kuchuja:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:201
msgid ""
"The job name (e.g. $Self-&gt;{'PostMaster::PreFilterModule'}-&gt;"
"{'JobName'}) needs to be unique!"
msgstr ""
"Jina la kazi (mf. $Self-&gt;{'MkuuWaPosta::ModuliUchujaji'}-&gt;"
"{'JinaKazi'}) linahitaji kuwa la kipekee!"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:206
msgid ""
"Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::Match is a default module to match on "
"some email header (e.g. From, To, Subject, ...). It can set new email "
"headers (e.g. X-OTRS-Ignore: yes or X-OTRS-Queue: spam) if a filter rule "
"matches. The jobs of the Example 7-2 can be inserted in <filename>Kernel/"
"Config.pm</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Kiini::Mfumo::MkuuWaPosta::Kichujio::Fananisha ni moduli chaguo-msingi kwa "
"ajili ya kufananisha baadhi ya vichwa vya barua pepe (mf. Kutoka, Kwenda, "
"Kichwa cha habari, ...). Inaweza kuseti vichwa vipya vya barua pepe (mf. X-"
"OTRS-puuza:ndiyo au X-OTRS-Foleni:barua taka) kama sheria ya kuchuja "
"imefanana. Kazi za Mfano 7-2 unaweza kuingizwa katika <filename>Kernel/"
"Config.pm</filename>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><example><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:210
msgid ""
"Example jobs for the filter module Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::Match"
msgstr ""
"Kazi za mfano kwa moduli ya kuchuja Kiini::Mfumo::MkuuWaPosta::Kichujio::"
"Fananisha"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><example><para><programlisting>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:214
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    # Job Name: 1-Match\n"
"    # (block/ignore all spam email with From: noreply@)\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{'PostMaster::PreFilterModule'}-&gt;{'1-Match'} = {\n"
"        Module =&gt; 'Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::Match',\n"
"        Match =&gt; {\n"
"            From =&gt; 'noreply@',\n"
"        },\n"
"        Set =&gt; {\n"
"            'X-OTRS-Ignore' =&gt; 'yes',\n"
"        },\n"
"    };\n"
"    # Job Name: 2-Match\n"
"    # (sort emails with From: sales@example.com and Subject: **ORDER**\n"
"    # into queue 'Order')\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{'PostMaster::PreFilterModule'}-&gt;{'2-Match'} = {\n"
"        Module =&gt; 'Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::Match',\n"
"        Match =&gt; {\n"
"            To =&gt; 'sales@example.com',\n"
"            Subject =&gt; '**ORDER**',\n"
"        },\n"
"        Set =&gt; {\n"
"            'X-OTRS-Queue' =&gt; 'Order',\n"
"        },\n"
"    };\n"
msgstr ""
"    # Job Name: 1-Match\n"
"    # (block/ignore all spam email with From: noreply@)\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{'PostMaster::PreFilterModule'}-&gt;{'1-Match'} = {\n"
"        Module =&gt; 'Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::Match',\n"
"        Match =&gt; {\n"
"            From =&gt; 'noreply@',\n"
"        },\n"
"        Set =&gt; {\n"
"            'X-OTRS-Ignore' =&gt; 'yes',\n"
"        },\n"
"    };\n"
"    # Job Name: 2-Match\n"
"    # (sort emails with From: sales@example.com and Subject: **ORDER**\n"
"    # into queue 'Order')\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{'PostMaster::PreFilterModule'}-&gt;{'2-Match'} = {\n"
"        Module =&gt; 'Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::Match',\n"
"        Match =&gt; {\n"
"            To =&gt; 'sales@example.com',\n"
"            Subject =&gt; '**ORDER**',\n"
"        },\n"
"        Set =&gt; {\n"
"            'X-OTRS-Queue' =&gt; 'Order',\n"
"        },\n"
"    };\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:244
msgid ""
"Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::CMD is a default module to pipe the "
"email into an external command. The output is given to STDOUT and if the "
"result is true, then set new email header (e.g. X-OTRS-Ignore: yes or X-OTRS-"
"Queue: spam). The Example 7-3 can be used in <filename>Kernel/Config.pm</"
"filename>"
msgstr ""
"Kiini::Mfumo::MkuuWaPosta::Chuja::CMD ni moduli chaguo-msingi ya kupeleka "
"barua pepe kwenda kwenye amri ya nje. Matokeo yanapewa kwa STDOUT na kama "
"majibu ni kweli, kisha seti kichwa kipya cha barua pepe (mf. X-OTRS-Puuza: "
"ndiyo au X-OTRS-Foleni: barua taka). Mfano 7-3 unaweza kutumika katika "
"<filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><example><title>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:248
msgid ""
"Example job for the filter module Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::CMD"
msgstr ""
"Kazi ya mfano kwa moduli ya kuchuja Kiini::Mfumo::MkuuWaPosta::Kichujio::CMD"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><example><para><programlisting>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:252
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    # Job Name: 5-SpamAssassin\n"
"    # (SpamAssassin example setup, ignore spam emails)\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{'PostMaster::PreFilterModule'}-&gt;{'5-SpamAssassin'} = {\n"
"        Module =&gt; 'Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::CMD',\n"
"        CMD =&gt; '/usr/bin/spamassassin | grep -i \"X-Spam-Status: yes\"',\n"
"        Set =&gt; {\n"
"            'X-OTRS-Ignore' =&gt; 'yes',\n"
"        },\n"
"    };\n"
msgstr ""
"    # Job Name: 5-SpamAssassin\n"
"    # (SpamAssassin example setup, ignore spam emails)\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{'PostMaster::PreFilterModule'}-&gt;{'5-SpamAssassin'} = {\n"
"        Module =&gt; 'Kernel::System::PostMaster::Filter::CMD',\n"
"        CMD =&gt; '/usr/bin/spamassassin | grep -i \"X-Spam-Status: yes\"',\n"
