#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/smime.xml:219
msgid ""
"Now that these operations have been performed, the S/MIME setup must be "
"completed in OTRS."
msgstr ""
"Sasa kwa kuwa hizi operesheni zimefanyika, kuseti S/MIME lazima kukamilike "
"katika OTRS."

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/smime.xml:223
msgid ""
"This part of the setup is carried out in the Admin page, choosing the link "
"<link linkend=\"adminarea-smime\">\"SMIME\"</link>. In case the general S/"
"MIME support in OTRS has not yet been enabled, the mask points this out to "
"the administrator and provides an appropriate link for enabling it."
msgstr ""
"hiki kipande cha kuseti kinafanyika katika ukurasa wa Msimamizi, kuchagua "
"kiungo <link linkend=\"adminarea-smime\">\"SMIME\"</link>. Ikiwa msaada wa S/"
"MIME wa kawaida kwenye OTRS haujawezeshwa, barakoa itanbainisha hii kwa "
"msimamizi na kutoa kiungo cha kuiwezesha."

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/smime.xml:227
msgid ""
"With the SysConfig group <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Crypt::"
"SMIME\">\"Crypt::SMIME\"</link>, you can also enable and configure the "
"general S/MIME support."
msgstr ""
"Na kundi la SysConfig <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Crypt::SMIME"
"\">\"Crypt::SMIME\"</link>, unaweza kuwezesha na kusanidi msaada wa ujumla "
"wa S/MIME."

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/smime.xml:231
msgid ""
"Here you can activate S/MIME support, and define the paths for the OpenSSL "
"command and the directory for the certificates. The key file created above "
"must be stored in the directory indicated here. Otherwise OpenSSL cannot use "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Hana unweza kuamilisha msaada wa S/MIME, na kufafanua njia za anri ya "
"OpenSSL na mpangilio orodha wa hati. Faili la ufunguo lililo tengnezwa hapo "
"juu lazima lihifadhiwe kwenye mpangilio orodha ulioonyeshwa hapa. La sivyo "
"OpenSSL haiwezi kulitumia."

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/smime.xml:235
msgid ""
"The next step is performed in the <link linkend=\"adminarea-smime\">S/MIME "
"configuration on the OTRS Admin page</link>. Here, you can import the "
"private key(s) of the OTRS system and the public keys of other communication "
"partners. Enter the public key that has been created in the beginning of "
"this section and added to OTRS."
msgstr ""
"Hatua inayofwata inafanywa kwenye <link linkend=\"adminarea-smime\"> usanidi "
"wa S/MIME katika ukurasa wa Msimamizi wa OTRS</link>. Hapa unaweza kuagiza "
"ufunguo binafsi wa (za) mfumo wa OTRS na funguo za umma za mawasiliano ya "
"wabia wengine. Ingiza ufunguo wa umma ambao umetengenezwa mwanzoni mwa "
"kifungu hiki na kuongezwa kwenye OTRS."

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/smime.xml:239
msgid ""
"Obviously, all public S/MIME keys of communication partners can be imported "
"using the <link linkend=\"adminarea-customers\">customer administration "
"tool</link> as well."
msgstr ""
"Kwa kawaida, funguo zote za umma za S/MIME za mawasiliano ya washiriki "
"zinaweza kuagizwa kwa kutumia <link linkend=\"adminarea-customers\">kifaa "
"cha usimamizi wa mteja</link> pia."

#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:6
msgid "Time related functions"
msgstr "Shughuli zinazoendana na muda"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:9
msgid "Setting up business hours, holidays and time zones"
msgstr "Kuseti masaa, sikuku na majira ya biashara"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:12
msgid ""
"Some functions in OTRS, like escalations and <link linkend=\"unlock-tickets"
"\">automatic unlocking of tickets</link>, depend on a proper configuration "
"of business hours, time zones and holidays. You can define these via the "
"<link linkend=\"sysconfig\">SysConfig interface</link>, in <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time\">Framework &gt; Core::Time</link>.  "
"You can also specify different sets of business hours, holidays and time "
"zones as separate 'Calendars' in <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:"
"Core::Time::Calendar1\">Framework &gt; Core::Time::Calendar1</link> through "
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time::Calendar9\">Framework "
"&gt; Core::Time::Calendar9</link>. Calendars can be defined by <link linkend="
"\"adminarea-queue\">queue settings</link>, or on SLA levels. This means "
"that, for example, you can specify a calendar with 5 x 8 business hours for "
"your 'standard' SLA, but create a separate calendar with 7 x 24 support for "
"your 'gold' SLA; as well as set a calendar for your 'Support-USA' queue with "
"a different time window than your 'Support-Japan' queue. OTRS can handle up "
"to 99 different calendars."
msgstr ""
"Baadhi ya kazi katika OTRS, kama upandishaji na <link linkend=\"unlock-"
"tickets\">kufungua kiotomatiki tiketi</link>, inategemea kwenye usanidi "
"sahihi wa masaa ya biashara, majira ya saa na sikukuu. Unaweza kufafanua hii "
"kupitia <link linkend=\"sysconfig\">Kiolesura cha SysConfig</link>, katika "
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time\">Kiunzi &gt; Kiini::"
"Muda</link>. Unaweza kuweka bayana seti tofauti za masaa ya kazi, sikukuu na "
"majira ya saa kama 'Kalenda' tofauti katika <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time::Calendar1\">Kiunzi &gt; Kiini::Muda::"
"Kalenda1</link> kupitia <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::"
"Time::Calendar9\">Kiunzi &gt; Kiini::Muda::Kalenda9</link>. Kalenda zinaweza "
"kufafanuliwa na <link linkend=\"adminarea-queue\">mipangilio ya foleni</"
"link>, au ngazi za SLA. Hii ina maanisha, kwa mfano, unaweza kuweka bayana "
"kalenda yenye masaa ya biashara 5 x 8 kwa SLA yako ya 'Kawaida', lakini "
"ukatengeneza kalenda tofauti ya msaada wa 7 x 24 kwa SLA zako za 'dhahabu'; "
"na pia kuseti kalenda kwa ajili ya foleni yako ya 'Msaada-USA' yenye dirisha "
"tofauti la muda tofauti na lile la foleni yako ya 'Msaada-Japan'. OTRS "
"inaweza kushughulikia mpaka kalenda tofauti 99."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:17
msgid "Business Hours"
msgstr "Masaa ya Biashara"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:20
msgid ""
"Set up the working hours for your system in SysConfig <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time:TimeWorkingHours\">Framework &gt; "
"Core::Time::TimeWorkingHours</link>, or for your specific calendar in the "
"calendar's configuration. OTRS can handle a granularity of one hour. "
"Checking the marks in the boxes 8, 9, 10 ... 17 corresponds with business "
"hours of 8 AM - 6 PM."
msgstr ""
"Seti masaa ya kazi kwa ajili ya mfumo wako katika SysConfig <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time:TimeWorkingHours\">kiunzi&gt; Kiini::"
"Muda::MudaMasaaYaKazi</link>, au kwa kalenda zako maalumu katika usanidi wa "
"kalenda. OTRS inaweza kushughulikia muda wa saa moja. Kuweka alama katika "
"visanduku 8, 9, 10 ... 17 inaendana na masaa ya kazi ya 8 asubuhi - 6 "
"alasiri."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:24
msgid ""
"Only during business hours can tickets escalate, notifications for escalated "
"and pending tickets be sent, and tickets be unlocked."
msgstr ""
"Katika masaa ya biashara tu ndio tiketi zinaweza kupanda, taarifa za tiketi "
"zilizopandishwa na tiketi zinazosubiri zinatumwa, na tiketi zinafunguliwa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:30
msgid "Fixed date holidays"
msgstr "Sikukuu zenye tarehe za kudumu"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:33
msgid ""
"Holidays that are on a fixed date every year, such as New Year's Day or the "
"Fourth of July, can be specified in <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time:TimeVacationDays\">TimeVacationDays</"
"link>, or in the corresponding section for the calendars 1-9."
msgstr ""
"Sikukuu ambazo ziko kwenye tarehe funge kila mwaka, kama Mwaka mpya au "
"tarehe nne ya Julai, zinaweza kubainishwa katika <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time:TimeVacationDays\">MudaSikukuuSiku</"
"link>, au katika sehemu husika kwa ajili ya kalenda 1-9"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:37
msgid ""
"Tickets will not escalate nor get unlocked on dates defined in "
"TimeVacationDays."
msgstr ""
"Tiketi hazitapandishwa wala kufunguliwa katika siku zilizofafanuliwa kama "
"MudaSikuZaSikukuu."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:42
msgid ""
"By default, OTRS ships with the <emphasis>German</emphasis> holidays "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Kwa chaguo-msingi OTRS inasafirishwa na sikukuu za <emphasis>German</"
"emphasis> zimesakinishwa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:49
msgid "TimeVacationDaysOneTime"
msgstr "MudaSikuZaSikukuuMaraMoja"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:52
msgid ""
"Holidays such as Easter that do not have a yearly fixed date but instead "
"vary each year, can be specified in <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time:TimeVacationDaysOneTime"
"\">TimeVacationDaysOneTime</link>."
msgstr ""
"Sikuku kama Pasaka ambazo hazima tarehe maalumu ya mwaka lakini badala yake "
"zinabadilika kila mwaka, zinaweza kubainishwa kwenye  <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::Time:TimeVacationDaysOneTime"
"\">MudaSikuZaSikukuuMaraMoja</link>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:56
msgid ""
"Tickets will not escalate and will not be unlocked on dates defined in "
"TimeVacationDaysOneTime."
msgstr ""
"Tiketi hazitapandishwa na hazitafunguliwa  katika tarehe zilizofafanuliwa "
"katika MudaSikuZaSikukuuMaraMoja"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:61
msgid ""
"OTRS does not ship with any One-Time holidays pre-installed. This means that "
"you need to add holidays, such as Easter or Thanksgiving, to the system when "
"configuring OTRS."
msgstr ""
"OTRS haisafirishwi na sikukuu yoyote ya Wakati-Mmoja ikiwa imesakinishwa. "
"Hii ina maanisha unatakiwa kuongeza sikukuu, kama Pasaka au Sikuku ya "
"Shukrani, kwenye mfumo wakati wa kusanidi OTRS."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:70
msgid "Automated Unlocking"
msgstr "Ufunguaji Otomatiki"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:73
msgid ""
"Locked tickets can be automatically unlocked by the system. This feature "
"might be useful if, for example, an agent has locked tickets that need to be "
"processed, but he can't work on them for some reason, say because he is out "
"of the office on an emergency. The automated unlock feature unlocks tickets "
"after a given time to ensure that no locked tickets will be forgotten, "
"thereby allowing other agents to process them."
msgstr ""
"Tiketi zilizofungwa zinaweza kufunguliwa kiotomatiki na mfumo. Hiki "
"kipengele kinaweza kuwa cha muhimu, kwa mfano, wakala amefunga tiketi ambazo "
"zinatakiwa kuchakatishwa, lakini hawezi kuzifanyia kazi kwa sababu fulani, "
"tuseme yuko nje ya ofisi kwa dharura. Kipengele otomatiki cha kufungua "
"kinafungua tiketi baada ya muda fulani kuhakikisha hakuna tiketi "
"zilizofungwa zitakazosahaulika, hivyo kuruhusu mawakala wengine "
"kuzichakatisha."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:77
msgid ""
"The amount of time before a ticket is unlocked can be specified in the <link "
"linkend=\"adminarea-queue\">queue settings</link> for every queue. The "
"module <filename>bin/otrs.UnlockTickets.pl</filename>, which is executed "
"periodically as a cron job, performs the automated unlocking of tickets."
msgstr ""
"Idadi ya muda kabla tiketi haijafunguliwa inaweza kuwekwa bayana katika "
"<link linkend=\"adminarea-queue\">mipangilio ya foleni</link> kwa kila "
"foleni. Moduli <filename>bin/otrs.UnlockTickets.pl</filename>, ambayo "
"inatekelezwa kwa kipindi fulani kama kazi ya mfumo iliyopangwa, inafanya "
"ufunguaji otomatiki wa tiketi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:81
msgid ""
"Notifications on unlocked tickets are sent out only to those agents that "
"have the queue with the unlocked tickets set in \"My queues\", and that have "
"activated the notification on unlocked tickets in their personal <link "
"linkend=\"user-preferences\">preferences</link>."
msgstr ""
"Taarifa kuhusu tiketi zilizofunguliwa zinatumwa nje kwa wale mawakala wenye "
"foleni zilizosetiwa tiketi zilizofunguliwa kwenye 'Foleni zangu', na wame "
"amilisha taarifa kwenye tiketi zilizofunguliwa katika <link linkend=\"user-"
"preferences\">mapendeleo</link> yao binafsi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:85
msgid "Tickets will be unlocked if all of the following conditions are met:"
msgstr "Tiketi zitafunguliwa kama masharti yote yafuatayo yamefikiwa:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:91
msgid ""
"There is an <emphasis>unlock timeout</emphasis> defined for the queue the "
"ticket is in."
msgstr ""
"Kuna <emphasis>muda wa mwisho wa kufungua</emphasis> umefafanuliwa kwenye "
"foleni ambayo tiketi imo."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:96
msgid "The ticket is set to <emphasis>locked</emphasis>."
msgstr "Tiketi imesetiwa  kuwa <emphasis>imefungwa</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:101
msgid "The ticket state is <emphasis>open</emphasis>."
msgstr "Hali ya tiketi ni <emphasis>wazi</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:107
msgid ""
"The unlock timer will be reset if an agent adds a new external article to "
"the ticket. It can be of any of the following types: <emphasis>email-"
"external</emphasis>, <emphasis>phone</emphasis>, <emphasis>fax</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>sms</emphasis>, or <emphasis>note-external</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Muda wa kufungua utasetiwa upya kama wakala akiongeza makala mpya ya nje "
"kwenye tiketi. Inaweza kuwa ya aina yoyote kati ya zifuatazo: "
"<emphasis>barua pepe-nje</emphasis>, <emphasis>simu</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>faksi</emphasis>, <emphasis>sms</emphasis>, au <emphasis>notisi-"
"nje</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:111
msgid ""
"Also, if the last article in the ticket is created by an agent, and a "
"customer adds another one, either via web or email response, the unlock "
"timer will be reset."
msgstr ""
"Pia, kama makala ya mwisho katika tiketi imetengenezwa na wakala, na mteja "
"akaongeza nyingine, aidha kwa kupitia majibu ya tovuti au barua pepe, muda "
"wa kufungua utasetiwa upya. "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/time.xml:115
msgid ""
"The last event that will reset the unlock timer is when the ticket is "
"assigned to another agent."
msgstr ""
"Tukio la mwisho ambalo lita seti upya muda wa kufungua ni pale tiketi "
"imegawiwa kwa wakala mwingine."

#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/administration/pdf-output.xml:4
msgid "Customizing the PDF output"
msgstr "Kugeuza kukufaa matokeo ya PDF"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/pdf-output.xml:7
msgid "This section handles the configurable options for PDF output in OTRS."
msgstr ""
"Hiki kifungu kinashughulikia machaguo yanayoweza kusanidiwa kwa ajili ya "
"matokeo ya PDF kwenye OTRS."

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/pdf-output.xml:11
msgid ""
"If you use the Print action from anywhere within the OTRS interface, it will "
"generate a formatted PDF file. You can deactivate this by modifying the "
"configuration parameter <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::PDF:"
"PDF\">PDF</link> to create HTML output instead."
msgstr ""
"Kama ukitumia kitendo cha Kuchapisha kutoka kokote ndani ya kiolesura cha "
"OTRS, itazalisha faili  lililoumbuizwa la PDF. Unaweza kulemaza hii kwa "
"kubadilisha usanidi wa parameta <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:"
"Core::PDF:PDF\">PDF</link> kutengeneza HTML badala yake. "

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/pdf-output.xml:14
msgid ""
"You can adjust the look of the files generated by OTRS by creating your own "
"logo and adding it to <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::PDF:"
"PDF::LogoFile\">PDF::LogoFile</link>. You can use <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::PDF:PDF::PageSize\">PDF::PageSize</link> "
"to define the standard page size of the generated pdf file (DIN-A4 or "
"Letter), and also <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::PDF:PDF::"
"MaxPages\">PDF::MaxPage</link> to specify the maximum number of pages for a "
"pdf file, which is useful if a user generates a huge output file by mistake."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kurekebisha muonekano wa mafaili yanayozalishwa na OTRS kwa "
"kutengeneza nembo yako na kuiongeza kwenye <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::PDF:PDF::LogoFile\">PDF::FailiLaNembo</"
"link>. Unaweza kutumia <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::PDF:"
"PDF::PageSize\">PDF::UkubwaWaKurasa</link> kufafanua ukubwa wa kawaida wa "
"faili la pdf linalozalishwa (DIN-A4 au barua), na pia <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Core::PDF:PDF::MaxPages\">PDF::KikomoKurasa</"
"link> kuweka bayana idadi ya kikomo cha juu cha kurasa kwa faili la pdf, "
"ambayo ni muhimu kama mtumiaji akizalisha faili kubwa kwa makosa."

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/pdf-output.xml:18
msgid ""
"The Perl CPAN modules PDF::API2 and Compress::Zlib must be installed for the "
"generation of pdf files. In many distributions they are available as "
"packages and can be easily installed, using the respective package manager. "
"In case this is not possible, they have to be installed with CPAN. For "
"further information about installing Perl modules, please refer to the <link "
"linkend=\"installation-of-perl-modules\">\"Installation of Perl modules\"</"
"link> section."
msgstr ""
"Moduli za Perl CPAN za PDF::API2 na Compress::Zlib lazima zisakinishwe kwa "
"ajili ya uzalishaji wa mafaili ya pdf. Katika usambazaji mwingi zinapatikana "
"kama vifurushi na vinaweza kusakinishwa kirahisi, kwa kutumia meneja "
"kifurushi husika. Ikiwa hii haiwezekani, inabidi zisakinishwe na CPAN. Kwa "
"taarifa zaidi kuhusu kusakinisha moduli za Perl, tafadhali pitia kifungu cha "
"<link linkend=\"installation-of-perl-modules\">\"Usakinishaji wa moduli za "
"Perl\"</link>."

#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface.xml:5
msgid "Generic Interface"
msgstr "Kiolesura cha Ujumla"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface.xml:7
msgid ""
"The OTRS Generic Interface consists of a multiple layer framework that lets "
"OTRS communicate with other systems via a web service. This communication "
"could be bi-directional:"
msgstr ""
"Kiolesura cha Ujumla cha OTRS kina matabaka mengi ya viunzi ambavyo "
"vinaruhusu OTRS kuwasiliana na mifumo mingine kupitia huduma ya tovuti. Haya "
"mawasiliano yanweza kuwa ya pande mbili."

#. type: Content of: <section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface.xml:13
msgid ""
"<emphasis>OTRS as Provider: </emphasis> OTRS acts as a server listening to "
"requests from the External System, processing the information, performing "
"the requested action, and answering the request."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>OTRS kama Mtoaji: </emphasis> OTRS inakuwa kama seva inasikiliza "
"maombi kutoka kwenye Mfumo wa Nje, inachakatisha taarifa, kufanya vitendo "
"vilivyoombwa, na kujibu maombi."

#. type: Content of: <section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface.xml:20
msgid ""
"<emphasis>OTRS as Requester: </emphasis> OTRS acts as a client collecting "
"information, sending the request to the Remote System, and waiting for the "
"response."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>OTRS kama Muombaji: </emphasis> OTRS inakuwa kama mteja inakusanya "
"taarifa, kutuma maombi kwa Mifumo ya Nje, na kusubiri majibu."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface.xml:30
#: en/content/administration/adminarea.xml:1953
msgid "Web Services"
msgstr "Huduma za Tovuti"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface.xml:32
msgid ""
"A Web Service is a communication method between two systems, in our case "
"OTRS and a Remote System."
msgstr ""
"Huduma ya Tovuti ni njia ya mawasiliano kati ya mifumo miwili, katika kesi "
"yetu ni OTRS na Mifumo ya Mbali."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface.xml:36
msgid ""
"The heart of the Web Service is its configuration, where it is defined what "
"actions the web service can perform internally (Operation), what actions the "
"OTRS request can perform Remote System (Invokers), how data is converted "
"from one system to the other (Mapping), and over which protocol the "
"communication will take place (Transport)"
msgstr ""
"Moyo wa Huduma ya Wavuti ni usanidi wake, ambapo imefafanuliwa vitendo "
"ambavyo huduma ya wavuti inaweza kufanya kwa ndani (Operesheni), vitendo "
"gani maombi ya OTRS inaweza kufanya Mfumo wa Mbali (Wachochezi), jinsi gani "
"data inabadilishwa kutoka mfumo mmoja kwenda mwingine (Kuunganisha), na "
"kupitia itifaki gani mawasiliano yatapita (Usafirishaji)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface.xml:42
msgid ""
"The Generic Interface is the framework that makes it possible to create Web "
"Services for OTRS in a predefined way, using already made building blocks "
"that are independent from each other and interchangeable."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:6
msgid "Ticket priorities"
msgstr "Vipaumbele vya tiketi"

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:9
msgid ""
"OTRS comes with five default priority levels that can be modified via the "
"\"Priorities\" link on the Admin page. When creating a customized list of "
"priorities, please keep in mind that they are sorted alphabetically in the "
"priority selection box in the user interface. Also, OTRS orders tickets by "
"internal database IDs in the QueueView."
msgstr ""
"OTRS inakuja na ngazi tano za chaguo-msingi la vipaumbele ambavyo vinaweza "
"kubadilishwa kupitia kiubgo \"Vipaumbele\" katika ukurasa wa Msimamizi. "
"Wakati wa kutengeneza orodha iliyogeuzwa kukufaa ya vipaumbele, tafadhali "
"weka akilini kwamba zimepangwa kwa alfabeti katika kisanduku cha kuchagua "
"kipaumbele katika kiolesura cha mtumiaji. Pia, OTRS ina agiza tiketi kwa "
"Vitambulisho vya ndani vya hifadhidata katika MuonekanoWaFoleni."

#. type: Content of: <section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:14
msgid ""
"As with other OTRS entities, priorities may not be deleted, only deactivated "
"by setting the Valid option to <emphasis>invalid</emphasis> or "
"<emphasis>invalid-temporarily</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Kama ilivyo kwa vyombo vingine vya OTRS, vipaumbele haviwezi kufutwa, "
"vinalemazwa tu kwa kuseti chaguo Halali kuwa  <emphasis>batili</emphasis> au "
"<emphasis>batili-kwa muda</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <section><important><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:20
msgid ""
"If a new priority was added or if an existing one was changed, you might "
"also want to modify some values in SysConfig:"
msgstr ""
"Kama kipaumbele kipya kimeongezwa au kama kilichopo kimebadilishwa, unaweza "
"kutaka kubadilisha baadhi ya thamani katika SysConfig:"

#. type: Content of: <section><important><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:24
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Core::PostMaster:"
"PostmasterDefaultPriority\"> Ticket:Core::Postmaster::"
"PostmasterDefaultPriority</link> - defines the default priority for all "
"incoming emails."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Core::PostMaster:"
"PostmasterDefaultPriority\"> Tiketi:Kiini::Mkuu wa posta::"
"MkuuwapostaKipaumbeleChaguo-msingi</link> - inafafanua kipaumbele chaguo-"
"msingi kwa barua pepe zote zinazoingia."

#. type: Content of: <section><important><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:27
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketPhone_Priority\"> Ticket:Frontend::Agent:"
"Ticket::ViewPhoneNew:Priority</link> - defines the default priority in the "
"New Phone Ticket screen for agents."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketPhone_Priority\"> Tiketi:Mazingira ya mbele::"
"Wakala:Tiketi::OnaSimuMpya:Kipaumbele</link> - inafafanua chaguo-msingi la "
"kipaumbele kwenye skrini ya Tiketi Mpya Simu ya mawakala."

#. type: Content of: <section><important><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:30
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewEmailNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketEmail_Priority\"> Ticket:Frontend::Agent:"
"Ticket::ViewEmailNew:Priority</link> - defines the default priority in the "
"New Email Ticket screen for agents."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewEmailNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketEmail_Priority\"> Tiketi:Mazingira ya mbele::"
"Wakala:Tiketi::OnaBaruapepeMpya:Kipaumbele</link> - inafafanua chaguo-msingi "
"la kipaumbele katika skrini ya Tiketi Mpya Baruapepe ya mawakala."

#. type: Content of: <section><important><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:33
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Customer::Ticket::ViewNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::CustomerTicketMessage_PriorityDefault\"> Ticket:Frontend::"
"Customer:Ticket::ViewNew:PriorityDefault</link> - defines the default "
"priority in the New Ticket screen in the Customer frontend."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Customer::Ticket::ViewNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::CustomerTicketMessage_PriorityDefault\"> Tiketi:Mandhari "
"ya mbele::Mteja:Tiketi::OnaMpya:KipaumbeleChaguo-msingi</link> - inafafanua "
"chaguo-msingi la kipaumbele katika skrini Mpya ya Tiketi katika mazingira "
"yambele ya Mteja."

#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:6
msgid "Ticket States"
msgstr "Hali za Tiketi"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:9
msgid "Predefined states"
msgstr "Hali zilizofasiliwa kabla"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:12
msgid ""
"OTRS allows you to change predefined ticket states and their types, or even "
"add new ones. Two attributes are important for a state: the state name and "
"the state type."
msgstr ""
"OTRS inakuruhusu kubadilisha hali ya tiketi iliyofafanuliwa tayari na aina "
"zake, au hata kuongeza mpya. Sifa mbili ni muhimu kwa ajili ya hali: jina la "
"hali na aina ya hali."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:16
msgid ""
"The default states of OTRS are: 'closed successful', 'closed unsuccessful', "
"'merged', 'new', 'open', 'pending auto close+', 'pending auto close-', "
"'pending reminder' and 'removed'."
msgstr ""
"Hali chaguo-msingi ya OTRS ni: 'imefungwa kwa mafanikio', 'imefungwa pasipo "
"mafanikio', 'unganishwa', 'mpya', 'wazi', 'inasubiri kufunga otomatiki+', "
"'inasubiri kufunga otomatiki-', 'inasumbiri kikumbusho' na 'ondolewa'."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:20
msgid "New"
msgstr "Mpya"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:22
msgid "Tickets are usually in this state when created from incoming e-mails."
msgstr ""
"Tiketi huwa katika hali hii kama zimetengenezwa kutoka kwenye barua pepe "
"zinazoingia."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:27
msgid "Open"
msgstr "Wazi"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:29
msgid "This is the default state for tickets assigned to queues and agents."
msgstr ""
"Hii ndio chaguo-msingi la hali ya tiketi zilizo chini ya foleni na wakala."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:34
msgid "Pending reminder"
msgstr "Kikumbusho kinachosubiri"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:36
msgid ""
"After the pending time has expired, the ticket owner will receive a reminder "
"email concerning the ticket. If the ticket is not locked, the reminder will "
"be sent to all agents in the queue. Reminder tickets will only be sent out "
"during business hours, and are repeatedly sent every 24 hours until the "
"ticket state is changed by the agent. Time spent by the ticket in this "
"status will still add towards the escalation time calculation."
msgstr ""
"Baada ya muda wa kusubiri kuisha, mmiliki wa tiketi atapokea kikumbusho cha "
"barua pepe kuhusu tiketi. Kama tiketi haijafungwa, kikumbusho kitatumwa kwa "
"mawakala wote kwenye foleni. Tiketi za ukumbusho zitatumwa tu katika masaa "
"ya biashara, na kurudia kutumwa kila masaa 24 mpaka hali ya tiketi "
"itakapobadilishwa na wakala. Muda uliotumika na tiketi katika hali hii "
"utajumlishwa kwenye  mahesabu ya muda wa kupanda."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:41
msgid "Pending auto close-"
msgstr "Funga otomatiki inasubiri-"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:43
msgid ""
"Tickets in this status will be set to \"Closed Unsuccessful\" if the pending "
"time has expired. Time spent by the ticket in this status will still add "
"towards the escalation time calculation."
msgstr ""
"Tiketi katika hali hii zitasetiwa kuwa \"Hazijafungwa Kikamilifu\" kama muda "
"wa kusubiri umeisha. Muda uliotumiwa na tiketi katika hali hii utaongezwa "
"kwenye mahesabu ya muda wa kupanda."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:48
msgid "Pending auto close+"
msgstr "Funga otomatiki inasubiri+"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:50
msgid ""
"Tickets in this status will be set to \"Closed Successful\" if the pending "
"time has expired. Time spent by the ticket in this status will still add "
"towards the escalation time calculation."
msgstr ""
"Tiketi katika hali hii zitasetiwa kuwa \"Zimefungwa Kikamilifu\" kama muda "
"wa kusubiri umeisha. Muda uliotumiwa na tiketi katika hali hii utaongezwa "
"kwenye mahesabu ya muda wa kupanda."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:55
msgid "Merged"
msgstr "Unganishwa"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:57
msgid "This is the state for tickets that have been merged with other tickets."
msgstr "Hii ni hali ya tiketi zilizounganishwa na tiketi nyingine."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:62
msgid "Closed Successful"
msgstr "Imafungwa kwa Mafanikio"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:64
msgid ""
"This is the end state for tickets that have been successfully resolved. "
"Depending on your configuration, you may or may not be able to reopen closed "
"tickets."
msgstr ""
"Hii ni hali ya mwisho kwa tiketi ambazo zimesuluhishwa kwa mafanikio. "
"Kutegemeana na usanidi wako, unaweza au usiweze kufungua upya tiketi "
"zilizofungwa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:69
msgid "Closed Unsuccessful"
msgstr "Imefungwa Pasipo Mafanikio"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:71
msgid ""
"This is the end state for tickets that have NOT been successfully resolved. "
"Depending on your configuration, you may or may not be able to reopen closed "
"tickets."
msgstr ""
"Hii ni hali ya mwisho kwa tiketi ambazo HAZIJASULUHISHWA kwa mafanikio. "
"Kutegemeana na usanidi wako, unaweza au usiweze kufungua upya tiketi "
"zilizofungwa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:78
msgid "Customizing states"
msgstr "Kugeuza hali kukufaa"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:80
msgid ""
"Every state has a name (state-name) and a type (state-type). Click on the "
"<link linkend=\"adminarea-status\">States</link> link on the Admin page and "
"press the button \"Add state\" to create a new state. You can freely choose "
"the name of a new state. The state types can not be changed via the web "
"interface. The database has to be directly modified if you want to add new "
"types or change existing names. The default state types should typically not "
"be modified as this can yield unpredictable results. For instance, "
"escalation calculations and the unlock feature are based on specific state "
"types."
msgstr ""
"Kila hali ina jina (jina-la-hali) na aina (aina-ya-hali). Bofya kwenye "
"kiungo <link linkend=\"adminarea-status\">Hali</link> katika kurasa ya "
"Msimamizi na kubonyeza kitufe \"Ongeza hali\" kutengeneza hali mpya. Unaweza "
"kuchagua kwa uhuru jina la hali mpya. Aina ya hali haiwezi kubadilishwa "
"kupitia kiolesura cha wavuti. Hifadhidata inabidi ibadilishwe moja kwa moja "
"kama utataka kuongeza aina mpya au kubadilisha majina yaliyopo. Aina chaguo-"
"msingi la hali halitakiwi kubadilishwa kwa kuwa inaweza kutoa majibu "
"yasiyotabirika. Kwa mfano, mahesabu ya upandaji na kipengele cha kufungua "
"kwa kutegemea aina maalumu ya hali."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:84
msgid ""
"The name of an already existing state can be changed, or new states added "
"through this screen. If the state \"new\" has been changed via the web "
"interface, this change also has to be configured via the config file "
"<filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename> or via the SysConfig interface. The "
"settings specified in the script below have to be modified to ensure that "
"OTRS works with the changed state for \"new\"."
msgstr ""
"Jina la hali iliyopo tayari linaweza kubadilishwa, au hali mpya "
"zilizoongezwa kupitia hii skrini. Kama hali \"mpya\" imebadilishwa kupitia "
"hiki kiolesura cha tovuti, haya mabadiliko pia lazima yafanyiwe  usanidi "
"kupitia faili la usanidi <filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename> au kupitia "
"kiolesura cha SysConfig. Mipangilio iliyowekwa bayana katika hati chini "
"lazima ibadilishwe kuhakikisha OTRS inafanya kazi na hali iliyobadilishwa "
"kwa ajili ya \"mpya\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><programlisting>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:89
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [...]\n"
"    # PostmasterDefaultState\n"
"    # (The default state of new tickets.) [default: new]\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{PostmasterDefaultState} = 'new';\n"
"\n"
"    # CustomerDefaultState\n"
"    # (default state of new customer tickets)\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{CustomerDefaultState} = 'new';\n"
"    [...]\n"
msgstr ""
"    [...]\n"
"    # PostmasterDefaultState\n"
"    # (The default state of new tickets.) [default: new]\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{PostmasterDefaultState} = 'new';\n"
"\n"
"    # CustomerDefaultState\n"
"    # (default state of new customer tickets)\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{CustomerDefaultState} = 'new';\n"
"    [...]\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:102
msgid "<emphasis>Script: Modifying the Kernel/Config.pm settings.</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>Hati: Kubadilisha mipangilio ya Kernel/Config.pm.</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
