#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:138
msgid ""
"Now it is possible to use the new state type you just created. After a state "
"has been linked with this new state type, the OTRS configuration also has to "
"be changed to ensure that the new state is usable. Just modify the following "
"options via SysConfig:"
msgstr ""
"Sasa inawezekana kutumia aina mpya za hali ulizotengeneza. Baada ya hali "
"kuunganishwa na hii aina mpya ya hali, usanidi wa OTRS pia unatakiwa "
"kunadilishwa kuhakikisha hali mpya inatumika. Badilisha machaguo yafuatayo "
"tu kupitia SysConfig:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:142
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketPhone_StateDefault\"> Ticket -&gt; Frontend::"
"Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew &gt; AgentTicketPhone###StateDefault </link> - "
"to define the default next state for new phone tickets."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketPhone_StateDefault\"> Tiketi-&gt; Mazingira ya "
"mbele::Wakala::Tiketi::OnaSimuMpya &gt;  WakalaTiketiSimu###HaliChaguo-"
"msingi</link> - kufafanua chaguo-msingi la hali inayofuata ya tiketi mpya za "
"simu."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:148
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketPhone_StateType\"> Ticket -&gt; Frontend::"
"Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew &gt; AgentTicketPhone###StateType </link> - to "
"define the available next states for new phone tickets."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketPhone_StateType\"> Tiketi -&gt; Mazingira ya "
"mbele::Wakala::Tiketi::OnaSimuMpya &gt; WakalaTiketiSimu###AinaHali</link> - "
"kufafanua hali zitakazopatikana kwa tiketi mpya za simu."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:154
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewEmailNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketEmail_StateDefault\"> Ticket -&gt; Frontend::"
"Agent::Ticket::ViewEmailNew &gt; AgentTicketEmail###StateDefault </link> - "
"to define the default next state for new email tickets."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewEmailNew:"
"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketEmail_StateDefault\"> Tiketi -&gt; Mazingira ya "
"mbele::Wakala::Tiketi::OnaBaruapepeMpya &gt; TiketiBaruapepe###HaliChaguo-"
"msingi</link> - kufafanua chaguo-msingi la hali inayofuata ya tiketi mpya za "
"barua pepe."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:160
