msgstr "<emphasis>Kielelezo: Kuongeza mteja.</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea.xml:503
msgid ""
"Customers can access the system by providing their username and password. "
"The CustomerID is needed by the system to identify the user and associated "
"tickets. Since the email address is a unique value, it can be used as the ID."
msgstr ""
"Wateja wanaweza kufikia mfumo kwa kutoa jina la mtumiaji na nywila. "
"Kitambulisho cha Mteja kinahitajika na mfumo kutambua mtumiaji na tiketi "
"zinazohusika. Kwa kuwa anwani ya barua pepe ni ya kipekee, inaweza kutumika "
"kama kitambulisho."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea.xml:508
msgid ""
"As with agents, groups and roles, customers can not be deleted from the "
"system, only deactivated by setting the Valid option to <emphasis>invalid</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>invalid-temporarily</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Kama ilivyo kwa mawakala, makundi na majukumu, wateja hawawezi kufutwa "
"kwenye mfumo, wanaweza kulemazwa kwa kuseti chaguo Halali kuwa "
"<emphasis>batili</emphasis> au <emphasis>batili-kwa muda</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea.xml:515
msgid "Customer Groups"
msgstr "Makundi ya Wateja"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea.xml:518
msgid ""
"Customer users can also be added to a group, which can be useful if you want "
"to add customers of the same company with access to one or a few queues. "
"First create the group to which your customers will belong, via the <link "
"linkend=\"adminarea-groups\">Group management module</link>. Then add the "
"<link linkend=\"adminarea-queue\">queues</link> and select the new group for "
"the queues."
msgstr ""
"Wateja watumiaji wanaweza pia kuongezwa kwenye kundi, ambayo itakuwa na "
"manufaa kama ukitaka kuongeza wateja wa kampuni moja wenye ufikivu kwa "
"foleni moja ua zaidi. Kwanza tengeneza kundi ambalo wateja wako watakuwa "
"wanachama, kupitia <link linkend=\"adminarea-groups\">Moduli ya kusimamia "
"kundi</link>. Kisha ongeza <link linkend=\"adminarea-queue\">foleni</link> "
"na chagua kundi jipya la foleni."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea.xml:522
msgid ""
"The next step is to activate the customer group support. This can be done "
"with the configuration parameter <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:"
"Frontend::Customer:CustomerGroupSupport\">CustomerGroupSupport</link>, from "
"the Admin SysConfig option. Using the parameter <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Frontend::Customer:CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups"
"\">CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups</link>, you can specify the default groups for "
"a newly added customer, so that every new account will be automatically "
"added to these groups."
msgstr ""
"Hatua inayofwata ni kuamilisha msaada wa kundi la mteja. Hii inaweza "
"kufanywa na parameta ya usanidi <link linkend=\"ConfigReference_Framework:"
"Frontend::Customer:CustomerGroupSupport\">MsaadaKundiLaMteja</link>, kutoka "
"kwenye chaguo la Msimamizi la SysConfig. Kutumia parameta <link linkend="
"\"ConfigReference_Framework:Frontend::Customer:CustomerGroupAlwaysGroups"
"\">MtejaKundiDaimaMakundi</link>, unaweza kubainisha makundi chaguo-msingi "
"kwa mteja mpya aliyeongezwa, ili kila akaunti mpya iongezwe kiotomatiki "
"kwenye haya makundi. "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea.xml:526
