#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:654
msgid ""
"To change or edit a dynamic field you must have at least one field defined, "
"select an already added field from the dynamic fields overview screen and "
"update its settings."
msgstr ""
"Kubadilisha au kuhariri sehemu inayobadilika lazima uwe na sehemu moja "
"iliyofafanuliwa, chagua sehemu ambayo tayari imejazwa kutoka kwenye skrini "
"ya mapitio ya sehemu zinazobadilika  na sahihisha mipangilio."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:659
msgid ""
"Not all the dynamic field settings can be changed, the Field type and Object "
"type are fixed from the selection of the field and they can't be changed."
msgstr ""
"Sio sehemu zote zinazobadilika zinaweza kubadilishwa, aina ya Sehemu na aina "
"ya Kitu zimefungwa kutoka kwenye machaguo ya sehemu na haziwezi kubadilishwa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:663
msgid ""
"It is not recommended to change the field internal name, but the label can "
"be changed at any time. If internal name is changed all \"SysConfig\" "
"settings that have a reference to that particular field needs to be updated "
"as well as user preferences (if defined)."
msgstr ""
"Haishauriwi kubadilisha jina la ndani la sehemu, lakini lebo inaweza "
"kubadilishwa mda wowote. Kama jina la ndani limebadilishwa mipangilio yote "
"ya \"SysConfig\" ambayo ina marejeo kwenye sehemu hiyo yanahitaji kusasishwa "
"na pia mapendeleo ya mtumiaji (kama imefafanuliwa)."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:672
msgid "Showing a Dynamic Field on a Screen"
msgstr "Kuonyesha Sehemu Inayobadilika kwenye Skrini"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:674
msgid ""
"To display a dynamic field on a particular screen there are two mandatory "
"conditions:"
msgstr ""
"Kuonyesha  sehemu inayobadilika kwenye skrini fulani kuna masharti mawili ya "
"lazima:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:679
msgid "The dynamic field must be valid."
msgstr "Sehemu inayobadilika lazima iwe halali."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:684
msgid ""
"The dynamic field must be set to 1 or 2 in the configuration of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Sehemu inayobadilika lazima isetiwe kuwa 1 au 2 kwenye skrini ya usanidi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:690
msgid "Follow these steps to show a dynamic field in a screen"
msgstr "Fuata hatua hizi kuonyesha sehemu inayobadilika katika skrini"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:694
msgid ""
"Be sure that the dynamic field is set to valid, you can see the validity of "
"the field from the dynamic field overview screen. Set to valid by editing "
"the field if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Kuwa na uhakika kwamba sehemu inayobadilika imesetiwa kuwa halali, unaweza "
"kuona uhalali wa sehemu kutoka kwenye skrini ya mapitio ya sehemu "
"inayobadilika. Seti kuwa halali kwa kuhariri sehemu kama ikihitajika."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:701
msgid ""
"Open the \"sysconfig\" and select \"Ticket\" from the dropdown list in the "
"Actions side bar located in the left part of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Fungua \"sysconfig\" na chagua \"Tiketi\" kutoka kwenye orodha kunjuzi "
"katika mwambaa upande wa Vitendo ulio katika upande wa kushoto wa skrini."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:706
msgid ""
"You can also search for \"DynamicField\" in the search box above or the "
"\"sysconfig\" key directly if you already know it."
msgstr ""
"Pia unaweza kutafuta \"SehemuInayobadilika\" katika kisanduku cha kutafuta "
"juu au ufunguo wa \"sysconfig\" moja kwa moja kama unaujua."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:713
msgid ""
"Locate the setting sub-group for the screen that you are looking for and "
"click on it. For example \"Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewPhoneNew\"."
msgstr ""
"Tambua mpangilio kundi dogo kwa skrini unayoitafuta na kibonyeze. Kwa mfano "
"\"Mazingira ya mbele::Wakala::Tiketi::OnaSimuMpya\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:719
msgid ""
"Search for the setting that ends with \"###DynamicField\". For example "
"\"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketPhone###DynamicField\"."
msgstr ""
"Tafuta mpangilio uanoishia na \"###SehemuInayobadilika\". Kwa mfano "
"\"Tiketi::Mazingira ya mbele::WakalaTiketiSimu###SehemuInayobadilika\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:725
msgid ""
"If the setting is empty or does not have the required dynamic field name, "
"click on the \"+\" button to add a new entry. For example Key: Field1, "
"Content: 1."
msgstr ""
"Kama mpangilio uko tupu au hauna jina linalotakiwa la sehemu inayobadilika, "
"bofya kwenye kitufe \"+\" kuongeza ingizo jipya. Kwa mfano Ufunguo: Sehemu1, "
"Maudhui: 1."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:729
msgid ""
"If the setting already has the dynamic field name listed be sure that is set "
"to \"1\" to display the field or to \"2\" to display it as mandatory."
msgstr ""
"Kama mpangilio tayari una orodha ya jina la sehemu inayobadilika kuwa na "
"uhakika kwamba imesetiwa kuwa \"1\" ili kuonyesha hiyo sehemu au kuwa \"2\" "
"kuonyesha kwa ulazima."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:735
msgid ""
"Save the configuration by clicking in the \"Update\" button and the bottom "
"of the screen and navigate to the screen where you want the field to be "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Hifadhi usanidi kwa kubofya katika kitufe cha \"Sasisha\" na chini ya skrini "
"na abiri kwenda kwenye skrini ambayo unataka sehemu ionyeshwe."

