msgstr ""
"Pia inawezekana kufafanua itifaki ya usafirishaji wa mtandao kwa \"OTRS kama "
"mtoaji\" na \"OTRS kama mwombaji\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:113
msgid ""
"Click on the \"Save\" button to register the new web service in the database "
"or click \"Cancel\" to discard this operation. You will now be returned to "
"the web service overview screen."
msgstr ""
"Bofya kwenye kitufe \"Hifadhi\" kusajili huduma mpya ya tovuti kwenye "
"hifadhidata au bofya \"Katisha\" kuchana na operesheni hiyo. Sasa "
"utarudishwa kwenye skrini ya mapitio ya huduma za tovuti."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:118
msgid ""
"If you already have a web service configuration file in YAML format you can "
"click on the \"Import web service\" button on the left side of the screen. "
"For more information on importing web services please check the next section "
"\"Web Service Change\"."
msgstr ""
"Kama  tayari una faili la usanidi wa huduma za tovuti katika umbizo la YAML "
"unaweza ku bofya kwenye kitufe \"Agiza huduma ya tovuti\" upande wa kushoto "
"wa skrini. Kwa maelezo zaidi ya  uagizaji wa huduma za tovuti tafadhali "
"angalia kifungu kinachofuata \"Badiisha Huduma za Tovuti\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:124
