#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:215
msgid ""
"The \"Export web service\" button gives you the opportunity to dump the "
"configuration of the current web service into a YAML file, to download it "
"and to store it on your file system. This can be specially useful if you "
"want to migrate the web service from one server to another, for example from "
"a testing environment to a production system."
msgstr ""
"Kitufe cha \"Hamisha huduma za tovuti\" kinakupa nafasi ya kuweka usanidi wa "
"huduma ya tovuti ya sasa kwenye faili la YAML, kulipakua na kuhifadhi katika "
"mfumo wako wa mafaili. Hii inakuwa na manufaa pale unapotaka kuhamisha "
"huduma za tovuti kutoka seva moja kwenda nyingine, kwa mfano kutoka kwenye "
"mazingira ya kupima kwenda mazingira ya uzalishaji."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><warning><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:223
msgid ""
"All stored passwords in the web service configuration will be exported in "
"plain text format."
msgstr ""
"Nywila zote zilizohifadhiwa katika usanidi wa huduma ya tovuti zitahamishwa "
"katika umbizo la nakala wazi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:228
msgid ""
"Right after clicking the \"Export web service\" button a save dialog of your "
"browser will appear, just like when you click on a file download link on a "
"web page."
msgstr ""
"Baada tu ya kubofya kitufe cha \"Hamisha huduma ya tovuti\" maongezi ya "
"kuhifadhi ya kivinjari yatatokea, kama vile ukibofya kiungo cha kupakua "
"kwenye kurasa za tovuti."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:233
msgid ""
"Each browser on each operating system has its own save dialog screen and "
"style.  Depending on the browser and its configuration it is possible that "
"no dialog is shown and the file is saved to a default directory on your file "
"system. Please check your browser documentation for more specific "
"instructions if needed."
msgstr ""
"Kila kivinjari katika kila mfumo endeshi kina skrini yake ya kuhifadhi "
"maongezi na aina. Kutegemeana na kivinjari na usanidi inawezekana kwamba "
"hakuna maongezi yanayo onyeshwa na faili linahifadhiwa kwenye mpangilio "
"orodha chaguo-msingi katika mfumo wako wa faili. Tafdhali pitia nyaraka ya "
"kivinjari chako kwa maelekezo zaidi kama inahitajika."

