#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:334
msgid ""
"Sometimes it is necessary to delete a web service completely.  To do this "
"you can press on the \"Delete web service\" button and a new dialog will "
"appear asking for confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Wakati mwingine ni lazima kufuta huduma ya tovuti kabisa. Kufanya hivi "
"unabonyeza kitufe \"Futa huduma ya tovuti\" na maongezi mapya yatatokea "
"kukuuliza uthibitisho."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:339
msgid ""
"Click on \"Delete\" to confirm the removal of the web service or on \"Cancel"
"\" to close the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Bofya \"Futa\" kuthibitisha uondoaji wa huduma ya tovuti au \"Katisha\" "
"kufunga maongezi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><warning><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:344
msgid ""
"Deleting a web service can't be undone, please be careful when deleting a "
"web service."
msgstr ""
"Kufuta huduma ya tovuti hakubadiliki, tafadhali kuwa makini wakati wa kufuta "
"huduma ya tovuti."

