msgid "Web Service Debugger"
msgstr "Kieuaji cha Huduma ya Tovuti"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:362
msgid ""
"The Debugger stores the log of a web service. In the debugger screen you can "
"track all the web service communications for either provider or requester "
"types."
msgstr ""
"Anaye eua anahifadhi batli ya huduma ya tovuti. Katika skrini ya kueua "
"unaweza kufwatilia mawasiliano yote ya huduma za tovuti kwa aidha aina za "
"mtoaji au muombaji."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:366
msgid ""
"When this screen is shown the request list starts to load. After the list is "
"fully filled you can choose one of the rows (that means a communication "
"sequence) to check its details. This details will appear in a box below."
msgstr ""
"Hii skrini ikionyeshwa orodha ya maombi inaanza kupakuliwa. Baada ya orodha "
"kujaa unaweza kuchagua moja ya safu mlalo (hii ina maana mlolongo wa "
"mawasiliano) kukagua undani wake. Maelezo haya yatatokea kwenye boksi chini."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:371
msgid ""
"You can narrow the communication list using the filter on the right part of "
"the screen. You can filter by:"
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kupunguza orodha ya mawasiliano kwa kutumia kichujio upande wa kulia "
"wa skrini. Unaweza kuchuja na: "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:377
msgid "Communication type (provider or requester)"
msgstr "Aina ya mawasiliano (mtoaji au mpokeaji)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:382
msgid "Date: before and / or after a particular date"
msgstr "Tarehe: kabla na / au baada tarehe fulani"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:387
msgid "The remote IP Address"
msgstr "Anuani ya IP ya mbali"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:392
msgid "A combination of all."
msgstr "Mjumuisho wa yote."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:397
msgid ""
"After filter settings are set, push the \"Refresh\" button and a new list "
"will be displayed meeting your search criteria."
msgstr ""
"Baada ya mpangilio wa kichujio kusetiwa, bonyeza kitufe cha \"Onyesha Upya\" "
"na orodha mpya itaonyeshwa inayofikia vigezo vya utafutaji wako."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:402
msgid ""
"Depending on the search criteria for the filters the new list could return "
"no results."
msgstr ""
"Kutegemea na vigezo vya utafutaji kwa vichujio orodha mpya inaweza isitoe "
"matokeo yoyote."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:407
msgid ""
"On the left part of the screen under the action column you can select \"Go "
"back to the web service\" or clear the debugger log by pushing the \"Clear\" "
"button.  This will open a dialog that ask you to confirm erasing of the log. "
"Click \"Clear\" in the dialog button to perform the action or click on "
"\"Cancel\" to close this dialog."
msgstr ""
"Upande wa kushoto wa skrini chini ya safuwima ya kitendo unaweza kuchagua "
"\"Rudi nyuma kwenye huduma ya tovuti\" au futa batli ya anaye eua kwa "
"kubonyeza kitufe \"Futa\". Hii itafungua maongezi yanayo kuuliza "
"kuthibitisha kufuta batli. Bofya \"Futa\" katika kitufe cha maongezi kufanya "
"kitendo au bofya \"Sitisha\" kufunga maongezi."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:413
msgid ""
"In the \"Request details\" section you can see all the details for the "
"selected communication. Here you can track the complete flow and check for "
"possible errors or confirm success responses."
msgstr ""
"Kwenye sehemu ya \"Undani wa maombi\" unaweza kuona maelezo yote ya "
"mawasiliano yaliyochaguliwa. Hapa unaweza kufuatilia mtiririko mzima na "
"kukagua kasoro zozote au kuthibitisha mafanikio ya majibu. "

