msgid "<emphasis>Figure: Web services change.</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>Kielelezo: Badilisha huduma ya tovuti.</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:473
msgid ""
"Like the other Generic Interface configuration screens such as Network "
"Transport, Operation, Invoker and Mapping, the initial configuration (add)  "
"screen will only present two options: \"Save\" and \"Cancel\". If the "
"configuration is re-visited, a new option \"Save and Finish\" will appear.  "
"The behavior of this feature is defined below."
msgstr ""
"Kama skrini nyingine za ujumla za Kiolesura cha usanidi kwa mfano "
"Usafirishaji wa Mtandao, Operesheni, Mchochezi na Muunganiko, skrini ya "
"usanidi (ongeza) wa awali itaonyesha machaguo mawili: \"Hifadhi\" na "
"\"Sitisha\". Usanidi ukirudiwa, chaguo jipya \"Hifadhi na Maliza\" "
"litaonekana. Tabia ya kipengele hiki imafafanuliwa chini."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:480
msgid ""
"\"Save\" will store the current configuration level in the database and it "
"will return to the previous screen to review your changes or to configure "
"deeper settings."
msgstr ""
"\"Hifadhi\" itahifadhi usanidi wa ngazi uliyopo kwa sasa kwenye hifadhidata "
"na itarudi kwenye skrini iliyopita kufanya mapitio ya mabadiliko uliyofanya "
"au kufanya usanidi wa mipangilio ya ndani."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:485
msgid ""
"\"Save and Finish\" will store the current configuration level in the "
"database and it will return to the previous screen in the configuration "
"hierarchy (to the immediate upper configuration level)."
msgstr ""
"\"Hifadhi na Maliza\" itahifadhi usanidi wa ngazi uliyopo kwa sasa kwenye "
"hifadhidata na itarudi kwenye skrini iliyopita kwenye mfumo wa viwango wa "
"usanidi (kwa ngazi ya juu inayofuata ya usanidi)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/genericinterface/genericinterface-webservice-gui.xml:490
msgid ""
"\"Cancel\" will discard any configuration change to the current "
"configuration level and will return to the previous screen in the "
