msgstr ""
"Usakinishaji wa kiendeshi cha hifadhidata ya Oracle kwenye Red Hat / CentOS"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:467
msgid ""
"If you want to deploy OTRS on an Oracle database, you'll need to compile and "
"install the <application>DBD::Oracle</application> database driver. This is "
"slightly more complicated than installing any of the other packages; this is "
"because Oracle is a proprietary database and Red Hat nor the CentOS project "
"are allowed to distribute drivers in their RPM repositories."
msgstr ""
"Kama unataka kutumia OTRS kwenye hifadhidata Oracle, utahitaji kukusanya-"
"zalisha na kusakinisha kiendeshi cha hifadhidata <application>DBD::Oracle</"
"application>. Hii ni ngumu kidogo kusakinisha zaidi ya vifurushi vingine; "
"hii ni kwasababu Oracle ni hifadhidata inayomilikiwa kibinafsi na si mradi "
"wa Red Hat wala Centos unaruhusiwa kusambaza viendeshi katika hifadhi zao za "
"RPM."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:472
msgid ""
"First of all, we'd need to install <application>gcc</application>, "
"<application>make</application> and <application>CPAN</application> so we "
"can compile and install the driver. Below you see the command on CentOS; on "
"other versions it might look a little different."
msgstr ""
"Kwanza kabisa tutahitaji kusakinisha <application>gcc</application>, "
"<application>make</application> na <application>CPAN</application> ili "
"tuweze kukusanya-zalisha na kusakinisha kiendeshi. Chini unaona amri katika "
"CentOS; katika matoleo mengine inaweza kuonekana tofauti kidogo. "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:478
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[root@otrs-centos6 otrs]# yum -y install gcc make \"perl(CPAN)\"\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"[root@otrs-centos6 otrs]# yum -y install gcc make \"perl(CPAN)\"\n"
"        "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:483
msgid ""
"The next step is to obtain and install the database client. For this you "
"would need to sign up for a free account at the Oracle website.  You can "
"download the drivers from this page: <ulink url=\"http://www.oracle.com/"
"technetwork/database/features/instant-client/index-097480.html\"> http://www."
"oracle.com/technetwork/database/features/instant-client/index-097480.html</"
"ulink> Please choose the Linux x86 or x86-64 version corresponding to the "
"architecture of your system. You can check this with the <command>uname -i</"
"command>.  It is either 'x86_64' for x86-64 or 'i386' for x86.  You should "
"download the packages 'Instant Client Package - Basic', 'Instant Client "
"Package - SQL*Plus', and 'Instant Client Package - SDK'. Save them to a "
"location on your disk.  Now as the root user you can install the packages "
"using the following command:"
msgstr ""
"Hatua inayofuata ni kupata na kusakinisha programu ya hifadhidata. Kwa hili "
"utahitaji kujiunga kwa ajili ya akaunti ya bure katika tovuti ya Oracle. "
"Unaweza kupakua viendeshi katika ukurasa huu: <ulink url=\"http://www.oracle."
"com/technetwork/database/features/instant-client/index-097480.html\"> http://"
"www.oracle.com/technetwork/database/features/instant-client/index-097480."
"html</ulink> Tafadhali chagua toleo la x86 au x86-64  la Linux kwa kutegemea "
"na muundo wa mfumo wako. Unaweza kukagua hili kwa kutumia <command>uname -i</"
"command>. Ni aidha 'x86_64' kwa ajili ya x86-64 au 'i386' kwa ajili ya x86. "
"Unatakiwa kupakua vifurushi 'Instant Client Package - Basic', 'Instant "
"Client Package - SQL*Plus', na 'Instant Client Package - SDK'. Zihifadhi "
"mahali kwenye diski yako. Sasa kama mtumiaji mzizi unaweza kusakinisha "
"vifurushi hivyo kwa kutumia amri ifuatayo:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:494
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[root@otrs-centos6 otrs]# yum install oracle-instantclient*\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"[root@otrs-centos6 otrs]# yum install oracle-instantclient*\n"
"        "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:498
msgid ""
"After this you should set two environment variables and compile the DBD::"
"Oracle driver. Again, perform these tasks as the root user. The steps are "
"outlined below. Please note that for briefness some lines outputted by the "
"commands have been removed."
msgstr ""
"Baada ya hii unatakiwa kuseti vishika nafasi vya mazingira viwili na kusanya-"
"zalisha kiendeshi cha DBD::Oracle. Kwa mara nyingine, fanya kazi hizi kama "
"mtumiaji mzizi. Hatua zimeorodheshwa chini. Tafadhali tambua kwa ajili ya "
"ufupisho baadhi ya mistari iliyotolewa na amri imeondolewa."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:503
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[root@otrs-centos6 otrs]# export ORACLE_HOME=/usr/lib/oracle/11.2/client64\n"
"[root@otrs-centos6 otrs]# export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$ORACLE_HOME/lib\n"
"[root@otrs-centos6 otrs]# cpan\n"
"cpan[1]> look DBD::Oracle\n"
"...\n"
"Fetching with LWP:\n"
"  http://www.perl.org/CPAN/authors/id/P/PY/PYTHIAN/CHECKSUMS\n"
"Checksum for /root/.cpan/sources/authors/id/P/PY/PYTHIAN/DBD-Oracle-1.62.tar.gz ok\n"
"Scanning cache /root/.cpan/build for sizes\n"
"DONE\n"
"...\n"
"Working directory is /root/.cpan/build/DBD-Oracle-1.62-ZH6LNy\n"
"[root@localhost DBD-Oracle-1.62-ZH6LNy]# perl Makefile.PL\n"
"...\n"
"[root@localhost DBD-Oracle-1.62-ZH6LNy]# make\n"
