#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:528
msgid ""
"Now you should edit the file Kernel/Config.pm to provide ORACLE_HOME.  The "
"next step is to configure OTRS using the web installer, as described <link "
"linkend=\"web-installer\">in this section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Sasa unatakiwa kuhariri faili Kernel/Config.pm kutoa ORACLE_HOME. Hatua "
"inayofuata ni kusanidi OTRS kwa kutumia kisakinishi cha tovuti, kama "
"ilivyoelezewa  <link linkend=\"web-installer\">katika hiki kifungu </link>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:537
msgid "Installing OTRS on a Debian or Ubuntu system"
msgstr "Kusakinisha OTRS kwenye mfumo wa Debian au Ubuntu"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><important><para>
#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:540
msgid ""
"Please install OTRS <link linkend=\"manual-installation-of-otrs\">from "
"source</link>, and do not use the OTRS packages that Debian/Ubuntu provides."
